Emalunga eMkhandlu (AM) waseWelsh akhatsatekile ngekutsi "abukeka njengebantfu labatsandza kudlala".
Kunekukhatsateka emkhatsini wema-AM lamanye mayelana nesiphakamiso sekutsi ligama lawo kufanele lishintjwe libe ngema-MWP (Member of Welsh Parliament).
Loku kwabangelwa tinhlelo tekugucula ligama leSigungu kutsi libe yiPhalamende yase Welsh.
Ema-AM kulo lonkhe luhlaka lwepolitiki akhatsatekile kutsi loko kungahle kubangele kutsi ahlekwe.
Umuntfu lolilunga le-AM welicembu lebasebenti utsi licembu lakhe liyakhatsateka, Lelibito lifana ne-Twp ne-Pwp.
Kulabafundzako labangekho e-Wales: Ngesi-Welsh, Twp kusho "kuhlanya" kantsi Pwp kusho "ludlame".
Lomunye umholi we-AM watsi licembu lakhe, njengobe libumbene, litiva lingakhululekile futsi selitfole letinye tindlela.
Umuntfu lowatiwa ngekutsi yi Welsh Conservative watsi licembu lakhe "livulekile" ngekugucula ligama, kepha wacabanga kutsi loku kungukuhlukunyetwa kwe-MWP ibe yi-Muppets.
Kulomongo, leligama lelitsi w ngesiWelsh liphinyiswa njengeleligama lelitsi u ngesiNgisi sase Yorkshire.
LiKhomishane leSigungu lelibukene nekusungula umtsetfo wekutsi kwentiwe lushintjo lolunjalo, litsi: Kuncuma kwekugcina mayelana nekucondzisa kubitwa kwe-AMs kuyintfo yemalunga.
Umtsetfo waHulumende wase Wales wanga-2017 uniketa emandla Umkhandlu wase Wales kutsi ugucule ligama lawo.
NgaJuni, lelikomidi lakhipha imiphumela yelucwaningo lolwentiwe emphakatsini mayelana nesiphakamiso lesatiwa kutsi sitfola kusekelwa lokukhulu kutsi sibitwe ngekutsi yiPhalamende yase Welsh.
Mayelana netindzaba tekubekwa kwalabantfu labamnyama, liKhomishane likhetsa emaWMP (Welsh Parliament Members), kepha inketho ye-MWP itfole kusekelwa lokukhulu ekubonisaneni kwemphakatsi.
Ema-AM abonakala afaka letinye tindlela, kepha umzabalazo wekufinyelela kuvumelana ungaphazamisa lomengameli, Elin Jones lohlose kwetfula lomtsetfosivivinyo wekugucula ngekhatsi kwemaviki lambalwa.
Lomtsetfo wetingucuko utawufaka ekhatsi letinye tingucuko endleleni lesigungu lesisebenta ngayo, kufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekungafaneleki kwebavoti kanye nekusungulwa kweluhlelo lwekukhetsa emakomidi.
Ema-AM atawutfola livi lekugcina mayelana nembuto wekutsi kufanele abitwe njani uma akhuluma ngemitsetfo.
