Tsunami neKutamatama Kwemhlaba E-Indonesia Kucedza Sichingi, Kubulala Emakhulu Ebantfu
Nasi sibonelo: Ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba eLombok, tinhlangano letingekho ngaphasi kwahulumende tangaphandle tatjelwa kutsi atisasetjentiswa.
Nanobe bantfu labangetulu kwa-10% baseLombok balahlekelwa tindlu tabo, kute simemetelo senhlekelele lesivela eveni lonkhe, lokungumphumela wekutfola lusito lwemave emhlaba.
Kunyenti lokubuhlungu kutsi, bayakwenta kucace kutsi abaceli lusito lwemave emhlaba, ngako-ke loku kuyintfo lematima, kusho Make Sumbung.
Nanobe i-Save The Children ibeka licembu labo kutsi liye ePalu, akukabonakali kutsi ngabe tisebenti tangaphandle tingasebenta yini kulendzawo.
Umkhulumeli we-National Disaster Response Agency, uMnumzane Sutopo, utsi tiphatsimandla tase-Indonesia tiyabuka simo ePalu kute tibone kutsi ngabe tinhlangano tangaphandle tivumelekile yini kufaka sandla ekunikeni lusito.
Njengobe i-Indonesia ichubeka nekutamatama kwemhlaba, solo ayikakulungeli kuhlangabetana netinkinga temvelo.
Nanobe tindzawo tekukhosela ema-tsunami takhiwe e-Aceh, akuvamile kutsi tibonwe kulenye indzawo.
Kungekho kwetindlebe tekwecwayisa nge-tsunami ePalu, nanobe sekunetindzaba tekwesatjiswa, kungenteka kube yimbangela yetingoti.
Ngaletinye tikhatsi, kuhamba emkhatsini wetigodzi letinyenti tase-Indonesia bekulukhuni.
Tinhlekelele temvelo tenta tintfo tibe matima kakhulu.
Tibhedlela letitfwele bantfu letibekwe eLombok kute tinakekele bantfu labashone kuletinyatselo, titfutsele ePalu, kodvwa kutawutsatsa emalanga lamatsatfu kutsi tifike kulendzawo lensha.
UMengameli Joko Widodo wenta kulungiswa kwesakhiwonchanti sase-Indonesia lesonakele kwaba yintfo lebalulekile emkhankasweni wakhe welukhetfo, futsi wasebentisa imali yakhe ekwakheni imigwaco kanye netitimela.
Kodvwa kuncane kwetimali lokubangele kutsi hulumende waMnu Joko angakhoni kubusa njengobe abhekene nelukhetfo lolutawulandzela.
Umnumzane Joko uphindze abhekane nekucindzetelwa lokukhulu lokubangelwa kungevani ngekwenkholo lokuchubekako e-Indonesia, lapho khona emalunga enkholo yemaSulumane lamanyenti asuke emukele inkholo lechubekako.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1 000 babulawa futsi emashumi etinkhulungwane abaleka etindlini tawo njengobe emacembu emaSulumane nemaKhristu alwa etitaladini, asebentisa tikhali, butjoki, imicibisholo kanye naletinye tikhali leticijile.
