Umlimi wahlaselwa futsi wabulawa yingulube emakethe lese ningizimu-mpumalanga yeChina, ngekusho kwemibiko yetindzaba tasekhaya.
Indvodza, lekhonjwe ngeligama layo lekutsiwa nguYuan, yatfolakala ifile inemsheko lowehlukile, inengati eceleni kwesibaya setingulube eLiupanshui Market lese Guizhou, eSouth China Morning Post ibika ngeLisontfo.
Umfuyi wetingulube ulungiselela kunika tingulube umjovo wekugoma emapulazini etingulube ngaMay 30, 2005 e-Xining esifundzeni saseQinghai, eChina.
Kubikwa kutsi wahamba nemzala wakhe besuka esifundzeni lesisedvute sase Yunnan ngeLesine kute ayotsengisa tingulube letingu-15 emakethe.
Ngakusasa, tihlobo takhe tatsi natifika tatfola kutsi ufile, tatsi natibona umnyango wesibaya setingulube usivulekile.
Watsi kulesigodzi kunengulube lenkhulu lenengati emlonyeni wayo.
Lucwaningo lwetemphilo lwacinisekisa kutsi lengulube lendvuna leyayinesisindvo lesingaba ngemaphawundi langu-550 yahlupha lomfuyi kwaze kwaba sekufeni, ngekusho kwemibiko.
Umzala wami unematsambo lagcwele ingati futsi abhidlikile, kusho umzala wakhe lowatiwa ngekutsi ngu Wu, njengobe acashunwe yi-Guiyang Evening News.
I-video yekugadza ikhombisa kutsi Yuan wangena emakethe nga-4:40 ekuseni ngeLesine kute ondle tingulube takhe.
Umtimba wakhe watfolakala ngemuva kwelihora.
Lesilwane lesasibulala lendvodza besingesiyo ya-Yuan nobe yemzala wakhe.
Umphatsi wemakethe watjela i-Evening News kutsi tingulube tivalelwe kute tingahlaseli labanye, ngesikhatsi emaphoyisa atfola bufakazi kulendzawo.
Umndeni wakaYuan netiphatsimandla tasemakethe kubikwa kutsi bayakhuluma ngekuniketwa sincephetelo sekufa kwakhe.
Nanobe kungakavami, kunetindzaba tekuhlaselwa bantfu tingulube.
Nga-2016, ingulube yahlasela umfati nendvodza yakhe ensimini yabo eMassachusetts, futsi lendvodza yalimala kakhulu.
Eminyakeni lelishumi leyendlulile, ingulube leyayinesisindvo lesingaba ngemaphawundi langu-650 yabamba umlimi waseWelsh yammisa emgodzini wakhe wesigwedla waze umfati wayo wesaba futsi wayicosha.
Ngemuva kwekutsi umlimi wase-Oregon adliwe tingulube takhe nga-2012, umlimi waseManitoba watjela i-CBC News kutsi tingulube ativami kuba neludlame kodvwa liphunga lengati lingasebenta njenge "trigger".
