Njengobe bekubikezelwe, iSiphepho Rosa saba butsakatsaka njengobe sasendlula emantini labandzako ngaselugwini lolusenyakatfo yeMexico.
Nobe kunjalo, Rosa utawubangela imvula lenkhulu letawugcwala yonkhe indzawo enyakatfo yeMexico kanye naseningizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika kulamalanga letako.
Rosa unemoya lonemandla langemamitha langu-85 ngelihora, Siphepho sesigaba 1, sicala nga-5 ekuseni ngeLisontfo ngesikhatsi saseMpumalanga, futsi sibekwe emakhilomitha langu-385 eningizimu-nshonalanga yePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Rosa kungenteka ahambe enyakatfo ngeLisontfo.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, i-Plough yacala kwakheka ngetulu kweLwandle lwePasifiki yacondza emphumalanga, ngaseNshonalanga ye-US.
Rosa utawuletsa imvula lengemashumi lamabili etinhlavu etincenyeni taseMexico ngeMsombuluko.
Ngemuva kwaloko, lomtfombo wetimvula letishisako lohlangana nemfula lotsi usondzele utawukhicita imvula lenkhulu leseNingizimu Nshonalanga kulemalanga letako.
Endzaweni yangakini, 1 kuya ku-4 wemanti emvula atawubangela tikhukhula letingaba yingoti, kugeleta kwetigadla kanye nekugedvuka kwemhlaba ehlane.
Umtfombo wemvula lophansi utawukhokhela linani lemvula lelisondzela kumasentimitha lamabili kuya kulamatsatfu ngelihora etindzaweni letitsite, ikakhulu eningizimu yeNevada nase Arizona.
Imvula lenkhulu lengaba ngemasentimitha lamabili kuya kulamane kulindzeleke kutsi yehle etindzaweni letiseNingizimu Nshonalanga, ikakhulu e-Arizona.
Tigodzi letinemanti lamanyenti tivela ngekwehla lokusheshako kwetimo ngenca yemvula lenkhulu.
Akukafaneli kutsi uhambe ngetinyawo ehlane ngenca yesisongo semvula yetitfwatfwa.
Tikhatsi letimatima tingenta kutsi umfula ube ngumfula lomkhulu futsi tiphepho tingenta kutsi kube nemoya lomkhulu kanye nelutfuli.
Leticheme letisondzela titakwenta kutsi kube nemvula lenkhulu endzaweni letsite ngaselugwini lwaseNingizimu California.
Kunemvula lenkhulu lengetulu kwelihhafu lelihhafu yensiba, lokungabangela kutsi kube netintfo letincane letingagcwala futsi nemigwaco ibe yinsika.
