Emalangeni lambalwa letako, kubandza lokusele kutawugcwala futsi kuphindze kusakateke.
Incenye lenkhulu yaseMelika lesemkhatsini kanye nasemphumalanga kulindzeleke kutsi ifudvute kusukela nga-Okthoba ngesivinini lesisakateka kuma-80s kusuka eSouth Plains kuya etindzaweni letiseNyakatfo Mpumalanga.
