Bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20 babukele inchubo yekutsetfwa kwelicala laBrett Kavanaugh.
Bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20 babukele inkhulumo lejabulisako ngaLesine leyetfulwa ngumuntfu lofuna kuba nguMengameli wemaJaji aseNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh kanye nalomfati lobekafaka licala lakhe ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi lokwenteka ngemnyaka wa 1980, Christine Blasey Ford, etinkundleni letisitfupha tebethelevishini.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, umzabalazo wetembusave uyachubeka, netindzaba te-TV tiphazamise luhlelo lwato lwekubika ngetintfo letingazange ticatjangelwe ngaLesihlanu: sivumelwano lesakhiwe nguSincumo sase-Arizona Jeff Flake kutsi i-FBI yente luphenyo lweliviki lonkhe ngaletinsolo.
Ford watjela Likomidi Lelitiko Letebulungiswa kutsi lomfati bekangakungabata ngalokuphelele kutsi Kavanaugh bekadakiwe futsi wetama kutfukula emcimbini wasesikolweni.
Kavanaugh, ekufakazeni kwakhe lokunemandla, watsi ucinisile ngalokuphelele kutsi loko akwentekanga.
Kungenteka kutsi bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-20.4 labakubika ku-Nielsen ngaLesihlanu, babukele.
Lenkapani ibeka silinganiso sebantfu labatsandza kufundza ku-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kanye ne-MSNBC.
Kubala lamanye ema-networks labeka loluhlelo akuzange kutfolakale masinyane, kufaka ekhatsi i-PBS, i-C-SPAN ne-Fox Business Network.
Nielsen abevame kuba nenkinga yekwati kutsi bangakhi bantfu labambona ehhovisi lakhe.
Kute sikubeke kahle loku, sibalo sebantfu labatsandza kubukela le-movie silingana nesibalo sebantfu labatsandza kubukela imidlalo yelibhola letinyawo nobe ema-Academy Awards.
I-Fox News Channel, lekukhulunywa ngayo kakhulu ngekusekela kukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh, ihola tonkhe tinhlelo ngebantfu labatigidzi letingu 5.69 ngesikhatsi selicala lonkhe lilanga, kusho Nielsen.
I-ABC yaba sesibili ngesibalo sebantfu labatigidzi letingu-3.26.
I-CBS inetigidzi letingu-3.1, i-NBC inetigidzi letingu-2.94, i-MSNBC inetigidzi letingu-2.89 kanye ne-CNN inetigidzi letingu-2.52, kusho Nielsen.
Bantfu bebajabula kakhulu ngemuva kwekutsetfwa kwelicala.
Flake bekangumuntfu lobalulekile kulomdlalo wangaLesihlanu.
Ngemuva kwekutsi lihhovisi le-Republican Party likhiphe sitatimende sekutsi utawuvota kusekela Kavanaugh, wabanjwa ngemakhamera e-CNN ne-CBS ngeLesihlanu ekuseni amemeta babhikishi ngesikhatsi etama kungena esikhungweni sekuhlola seKomidi yeTemtsetfo.
Wema phansi imizuzu lembalwa ngesikhatsi ahlekwa, kwaboniswa ku-CNN.
"Ngime embikwakho", kwasho lomunye wesifazane.
Ucabanga kutsi ukhuluma liciniso yini kulelive?
Watjelwa kutsi, "Unamandla lapho kunebantfu labasikati labanyenti labangakhoni kusita".
Flake watsi lihhovisi lakhe selikhiphe sitatimende futsi watsi, ngaphambi kwekutsi lelifasitelo livalwe, kunalokunyenti lokudzingeka kutsi akutjele umhlangano welikomidi.
I-TV netindzawo tekusakata tonkhe tibe khona ngekushesha ngemuva kwema-awa lambalwa, ngesikhatsi liKomidi Letebulungiswa litawukhetsa kuchuba kukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh kulo lonkhe liKhomishane kute livote.
Kodvwa Flake watsi utawenta loko kuphela uma ngabe FBI itawuhlola emacala lamelene nalomuntfu lotawukhetfwa kuleliviki lelitako, njengobe bacela emaDemocrats lamancane.
Flake wacinisekiswa kancane ngekucoca nemngani wakhe, Sincumo selibandla lelibuswa yiDemocratic, Chris Coons.
Ngemuva kwekukhuluma naCoons kanye netikhulu letinyenti, Flake wenta sincumo sakhe.
Kukhetsa kwaFlake kunemandla, ngobe bekucinisekile kutsi emaRephabliki angeke abe nelilungelo lekuvuma Kavanaugh ngaphandle kweluphenyo.
Mengameli Trump uvule luphenyo lwe-FBI ngetinsolo letibhekiswe kuKavanaugh.
