Licembu lema-separatist labegcoke buso labagcinwe ngemaphoyisa ekuvimbela kudideka labagwaza ngemacandza futsi lahlanyela umbala lonenkhala, lokwakha litulu lelimnyama lelimnyama etitaladini lebetivame kugcwala tivakashi.
Kwaphindze kwaba nekulwa ngemuva kwaloko ngalelo langa, futsi emaphoyisa asebentisa tindvuku tawo kute alawule loko kucabana.
Kwaphela ema-awa lamaningi emacembu lancusa inkhululeko amemeta atsi "Ungakhohlwa, kute kutsetselelwa" abhekene nebacashi betinyunyana lababetsi "Phila iSpain".
Bantfu labangu-14 batfola kwelashwa ngenca yetilondza letincane labatitfola kulombhikisho, kusho bomagazini basekhaya.
Tinkinga tiyachubeka nekukhula kulendzawo lefuna inkhululeko, umnyaka munye ngemuva kwencwadzi yelinyenti ya-Okthoba 1 lebeyibekwe yiMadrid kutsi ingekho emtsetfweni kepha yagujwa ngema Catalan lahlukene.
Bavoti bakhetsa kuba ngulabazimele, nanobe linani lebavoti beliphansi ngenca yekuphikisana nekuhlukaniswa futsi labanyenti bebakhetsa kungahlanganyeli.
Ngekusho kwebaphatsi baseCatalan, bantfu labangaba ngu-1 000 balimala emnyakeni lowengcile ngemuva kwekutsi emaphoyisa etame kumisa kuvota e-TPS esifundzeni sonkhe.
Emacembu laphikisako ngekukhululeka ahlala busuku bonkhe ngaLesihlanu kute avimbele umbhikisho wekwesekela emaphoyisa avelonkhe.
Umhlangano wachubeka kodvwa baphocelelwa kutsi batsatse lenye indlela.
Narcis Termes, 68, umshina wetekukhibika lowaya emkhankasweni wekuhlukanisa nemkakhe utsi akasenawo litsemba ngelitsemba lekutsi iCatalonia itotfola inkhululeko.
"Lomnyaka lophelile saba nesikhatsi lesihle kakhulu.
Ngibona batali bami bakhala ngenca yekujabula ngekukhetsa, kodvwa nyalo sesibambekile", kusho yena.
Nanobe baphumelele kuncoba lokuncane elukhetfweni lwasekhaya lwangaDisemba, emacembu laphikisako ngekukhululeka eCatalan alwa kamatima kute agcine umfutfo wawo kulomnyaka nanobe baholi bawo labanyenti labatiwa kakhulu, labahlala ekudzingisweni nobe labavalelwe ejele balindzele kulahlwa, ngendzima yabo ekuhleleni inhlolovo kanye nekumenyetelwa kwekukhululeka.
Joan Puig, longumshayeli wemoto loneminyaka lengu-42 budzala lowabhala imibhikisho ngelucingo lwakhe kute asekele emaphoyisa, utsi lemphi yacalwa bosopolitiki emaceleni omabili.
Watsi: "Kucinisa kakhulu nyalo.
NgaMgcibelo, Oriol Junqueras, munye webantfu labatsatfu labadvonse umholi waseCatalan ejele kusukela ekupheleni kwemnyaka lophelile, wamemetela kutsi utawutiphakamisa elukhetfweni lwePhalamende yaseYurophu lwangamnyaka lotako.
Kuma njengemuntfu lofuna kuba lilunga lelikhetfo laseYurophu yindlela lencono yekugceka kubuyela emuva emagugu entsandvo yelinyenti kanye nekucindzetelwa lesikubonile kuhulumende waseSpain", kusho yena.
