Kubhodla kwenteka eceleni kwe Bestwood Street kanye ne Evelyn Street, umgwaco lohambela bantfu labanyenti eDepford, eningizimu-mpumalanga yelidolobha, cishe nga 10:15 BST.
Umshayeli wemoto wayimisa futsi kweta bomake, kodvwa lomuntfu wafa.
Lokushayisana kwenteka ngemuva kwetinyanga letimbalwa lomunye umgibeli ashone engotini yekushayisana ashayisana naChilders Street, lokungaba likhilomitha linye kusuka lapho ashayisana khona ngaMgcibelo.
Emaphoyisa aseMetropolitan atsi tisebenti tenta konkhe lokusemandleni ato kute titfole kutsi ngubani lomuntfu futsi titjele umndeni wakhe.
Imigwaco ivaliwe futsi kubekwe indlela yekuhamba kwemabhasi, futsi bashayeli betimoto bayalwa kutsi bayigweme lendzawo.
Tigebengu letisitfupha tilimatile
Tisebenti letisitfupha tilimatile ngesikhatsi kunesiphitsiphitsi ejele leligadziwe lemadvodza, kusho lihhovisi le-LSAP.
Kwaba nekucitseka lokukhulu ejele laseHMP Long Lartin eWorcestershire nga 09:30 BST (GMT+0100) ngeLisontfo futsi solo kuyachubeka.
Emaphoyisa aseTornado asevele atfutsele khona kute ayosebenta ngaloluhlelo, lolubandakanya tiboshwa letisiphohlongo futsi lolwenteka eceleni kwesakhiwo.
Letiphatsimandla talashwa endzaweni yesigameko ngenca yetilondza letincane ebusweni.
Sikhulumi selijele satsi: Tisebenti leticeceshwe ngalokukhetsekile setitfunyelwe kutawubukana nalesenteko lesenteka ejele laseHMP Long Lartin.
Emaphoyisa lasitfupha alashwa ngenca yekulimala.
Asikuvumelani nebudlova kulelijele, futsi kuyacaca kutsi labo labatiphatsa kabi batawuniketwa emaphoyisa futsi kungenteka bacashwe sikhatsi lesidze.
Ijele i-HMP Long Lartin ligcina tiboshwa letingetulu kwa-500, lokufaka ekhatsi letinye tetiboshwa letiyingoti kakhulu.
NgaJune kwabiketelwa kutsi umphatsi welijele usesibhedlela ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa siboshwa.
Nga-October emnyakeni lowengcile, emaphoyisa labukene nekuhlukunyetwa abitwa kutsi atewuphatsa inhlekelele lebeyenteka ngesikhatsi sisebenti sasesigodzini sihlaselwa ngebhola.
Siphepho Rosa Sitsembisa Kutsi Phoeniks, Las Vegas, Salt Lake City, kutawuba Netikhukhula Letinkhulu
Kucindzeteleka lokukhulu lokuhlasela i-Arizona kuyintfo lengavami, kodvwa nguloko lokungenteka kutsi kwenteke ekucaleni kweliviki lelitako ngobe emandla lasalako eSiphepho Rosa adlula ehlane lelingaseningizimu-nshonalanga, lokwenta kube netingoti tekukhukhula.
I-National Weather Service ikhiphe secwayiso setikhukhula ngeMsombuluko nangoLesibili endzaweni yase Arizona leseNshonalanga kuya eningizimu yeNevada, eningizimu-mpumalanga ye California nase Utah, kufaka ekhatsi emadolobha ase Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas, nase Salt Lake City.
Rosa kulindzeleke kutsi acondze ngqo e-Phoenix ngaLesibili, utawushaya ngeMsombuluko ebusuku ahambisane nemvula.
Umsebenti Wetikhatsi Wesive ePhoenix ubhale ku-Twitter kutsi kube netiphepho letingu-10 kuphela letingaba netiphepho letishisako nobe tibe nekucindzeteleka lokukhulu endzaweni lengemakhilomitha langu-200 kusuka ePhoenix kusukela nga-1950!
Katrina (1967) kwaba sivunguvungu lesingemamayela langu-40 kusuka e-AZ.
Umshini wekuhlola wetiphepho letinsha ungakhona kubikezela 2 kuya ku 4 wemali yemvula lencane lefika ku 6 wemali eMogollon Rim eArizona.
Letinye tindzawo letise ningizimu nshona, kufaka ekhatsi iRocky Central kanye ne Great Basin, kungenteka kutsi tibe ngu 1 kuya ku 2 wemali, kantsi kungenteka kutsi tibe ngu 4 wemali.
Kulabo labasendzaweni lengakakhukhumuki, imvula yemaRosa ingaba sibusiso ngobe indzawo yabo inematfuba lamanyenti ekoma.
Nanobe tikhukhula tingumsebenti lomkhulu, lokunisela lokuncane kungenteka kube lusito ngobe nyalo tindzawo letiseningizimu-nshonalanga tibhekene nesomiso.
Ngekusho kwe-U.S. National Drought Observatory, cishe emaphesenti langu-40 emave ase-Arizona abhekene nesomiso lesincane kakhulu, lokuyinhlobo yesibili lenkhulu, kubika i- weather.com.
Kwekucala, indlela yaRosa yacondza eveni lelisemphumalanga yeBaja California, enhlonhlweni yaseMexico.
Rosa, bekasesimeni lesicinile ngeLisontfo ekuseni, nemoya lonemandla langemakhilomitha langu-85 ngelihora, emamayela langu-385 enyakatfo yePunta Eugenia, eMexico futsi uya enyakatfo ngemamayela langu-12 ngelihora.
Lesiphepho sahlangana nemanti labandzako asePacific futsi saba nemandla lamancane.
Ngako-ke, kulindzeleke kutsi ifike eMexico ibe sivunguvungu lesinemandla ngeMsombuluko ntsambama nobe ebusuku.
Kunemvula lenkhulu etindzaweni letinyenti taseMexico, lokwenta kube netinkinga tetikhukhula
Imvula lephelele lengaba ngemasentimitha lamatsatfu kuya kulasitfupha kulindzeleke kutsi yehlele endzaweni yase Baja California kuya endzaweni lese ningizimu nshona yase Sonora, kungenteka inyuke ibe ngemasentimitha lalishumi, kusho i-weather.com.
Rosa utawuhamba enyakatfo acondze eMexico njengesiphepho lesishisako ngaphambi kwekutsi afike emnyeleni wase Arizona ekuseni ngaLesibili njengesifutfo lesibandzako, lesitawuhamba sidlule eArizona siye eningizimu ye Utah ngeLesibili ebusuku.
Ingoti lenkhulu lengabangelwa nguSiphepho Rosa nobe lokusele kwaso, yimvula lenkhulu kakhulu eBaja California, enyakatfo-nshonalanga yeSonora, kanye naseNingizimu-nshonalanga yase-U.S.  kusho i-National Hurricane Center (NHC).
