Bantfu labanyenti bafa ngenca yekutamatama kwemhlaba kanye netimvula letinkhulu letenteka e-Indonesia.
Lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa, labanyenti bagcumkela ngesikhatsi emagagasi lamakhulu ashaya lwandle ngesikhatsi kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwesabekako kanye neluswatfu kuhlasela sifundza sase-Indonesia i-Sulawesi, kusho tiphatsimandla ngeMgcibelo.
Emakhulu ebantfu ahlangana emcimbini lobekufanele wentiwe elugwini lolusePalu ngaLesihlanu ngesikhatsi emagagasi laphakeme ngemamitha langu-18 abhubhisa lolwandle nakushona lilanga, kwabulala bantfu labanyenti futsi kwabhubhisa konkhe lokwakwendlula.
Kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwalandzela.
Ngesikhatsi kusongelwa kwa-tsunami kukhula itolo, bantfu bebasolo benta imisebenti yabo elugwini futsi abazange babaleke ngekushesha baze baba netisulu, kusho Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, sikhulumi se-BNPB ngesikhatsi semhlangano eJakarta.
"Lentfutfu-mhlaba ayizange ite yodvwa, yahudvula timoto, tingodvo, tindlu, yashaya konkhe lokwakusendzaweni", kusho Nugroho, futsi wachubeka watsi le-tsunami yayihamba elwandle ihamba ngemahora langu-497 ngaphambi kwekutsi ishaye lolwandle.
Watsi labanye bantfu bebakhuphukela etihlahleni kute baphephe ema-tsunami futsi baphile.
Bantfu labangu-16,700 bahamba baya etindzaweni letingu-24 tekusebentela ePalu.
Titfombe letakhishwa yi-BNPB tikhombisa takhiwo letinyenti nemabhizinisi labhujisiwe, emabhuloho lagobene futsi abhidlika kanye nemasontfo labekwe emantini.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokulandzelanako kwanyakazisa lidolobha lelisogwini loluseningizimu ne-Alaska ngaMgcibelo.
Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwabonakala endzaweni lenebantfu labatigidzi letingu-2,4
I-BPPT yatsi ngekusho kwayo, emandla lakhishwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu ngaLesihlanu abenemandla langetulu kwa-200 kunemandla ekuhlasela kwebhomu le-athomu lelahlwa eHiroshima eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Lendzawo lephakeme ledvutane nelidolobha, ingenta kutsi kube nemtsunami lomkhulu.
Nugroho uchaza lomonakalo ngekutsi "ubukhulu" futsi utsi tinkhulungwane tetindlu, tibhedlela, timakethe kanye nemahhotela kubhujisiwe.
Watsi, imitimba yalabanye bantfu yatfolwa ibhajwe ngaphansi kwetakhiwo letibhidlitiwe, futsi wachubeka watsi bantfu labangu-540 balimala kantsi labangu-29 babete lutfo.
Nugroho utsi kufa nekulimala kungenteka kube kukhulu ngaselugwini lwemkhumbi longemakhilomitha langu-300 (190 ema-mile) enyakatfo yePalu, endzaweni lebitwa ngekutsi yiDonggala, lesedvute nendzawo lokuchamuka kuyo kutamatama kwemhlaba.
Kutsintsana kuvaleke kakhulu ngenca yekweswela lwati lolusuka kuDonggala, kusho Nugroho.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-300 000 bahlala lapho, kusho i-Red Cross esitatimendeni, yengeta ngekutsi emalunga ayo kanye netisebenti letititsandzako baya etindzaweni letineliphutsa.
"Loku kuyinhlekelele, kodvwa kungaba kubi kakhulu", washo njalo.
NgaLesihlanu, lelitiko latfola kugceka lokukhulu ngekungatjeli bantfu kutsi kukhona tsunami lebeyitawuhlaselwa yiPalu, nanobe tiphatsimandla tatsi lamagagasi abesavele ahlaselwa ngesikhatsi kukhishwa lesecwayiso.
Umfanekiso lowatfolakala ku-social media ukhombisa indvodza lesetulu kwesakhiwo ikhala ngekwesaba kutsi kutawugadla tsunami, ibhekise kubantfu labasemgwacweni longentasi.
Kungakapheli nemizuzu lembalwa, emanti agcwala agcwala elusentseni lwelwandle, ahamba netakhiwo kanye netimoto.
