I-USA kufanele iphindze ikhulise imali yayo yekusekela i-AI.
Njengobe iChina isebenta kakhulu kutekuhlakanipha, iMelika kufanele iphindzaphindze imali letawusetjentiswa ekucwaningeni ngaloluhlobo, kusho umtsengi kanye nemuntfu lowenta umsebenti we-A2 Kai-Fu Lee, losebente ku-Google, Microsoft kanye ne-Apple.
Letimphendvulo tavela ngemuva kwekutsi tincenye letehlukene tahulumende waseMelika tenta simemetelo nge-AI, ngisho nalapho i-USA yonkhe ingenaso siteshi se-AI.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, iChina yetfula luhlelo lwayo emnyakeni lowengcile: ihlose kuba ngulenombolo yekucala kutintfo letinsha te-AI nga-2030.
"Kuphindza kabili imali yelucwaningo lwe-AI kusicalo lesihle, uma ucabanga kutsi onkhe lamanye emave ahamba ngemuva kwe-US, futsi sifuna kutfola lokulandzelako lokutawutfutfukisa i-AI", kusho Lee.
Kwengeta imali kungenta kube matima kutsi kube khona lokunye lokwentiwa yi-AI eMelika, Lee watjela i-CNBC ngelusuku lwaLesihlanu.
Lea, umnikazi wencwadzi letsi AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and New World Order" ishicilelwe kulenyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, umphatsi we Sinovation Ventures, losatjala imali kulenye yetinkampani letihamba phambili te-AI eChina, i-Face++.
Ngemnyaka wa 1980 e Carnegie Mellon University wakha luhlelo lwe AI lolwabulala badlali labakhulu base America labadlala i Othello, ngemuva kwaloko waba ngumholi we Microsoft Research kanye nemengameli we Google China.
Lee wavuma umncintiswano wetekuhweba we U.S. hulumende njengaloku i-Robotics Challenge ye-Advanced Defense Research Project futsi wabuta kutsi lomsebenti lolandzelako utawentiwa nini, kute kusitwe kutfola umboniswa lolandzelako.
Lee utsi bacwaningi baseMelika bavame kusebenta kamatima kute batfole umklomelo kuHulumende.
"Akuyona iChina leyakha baholi betemfundvo; kungumsebenti", kusho Lee.
Facebook, iGoogle kanye naletinye tinkampani tebucwepheshe tisebentise bantfu labasemanyuvesi ekucwaningeni nge-AI kuleminyaka lembalwa leyengcile.
Lee watsi kugucuka kwenchubomgomo yetekufika kungaphindze kusite i-USA kutsi isekele imitamo lemayelana ne-AI.
"Ngicabanga kutsi likhadi leliluhlata linganiketwa ngekushesha kulabo labane-PhD ku-AI", washo.
Umkhandlu Wesive wase China wakhipha Luhlelo Lwekutfutfukisa Luhlelo Lwekwenta Lwati Lweluhlobo Lolulandzelako ngaJulayi 2017.
I-China Natural Science Foundation iniketa bantfu imali etikhungweni temfundvo ngendlela lefanako ne-Natural Science Foundation kanye naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende letiniketa bacwaningi baseMelika imali, kodvwa lizinga lemsebenti wetemfundvo lisezingeni leliphansi eChina, kusho Lee.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka e-U.S. Litiko Letekuvikela lakha i-Artificial Intelligence Collaborative Center, lebeyihlose kufaka balingani betimboni netemfundvo, futsi i-White House yamemetela kwakhiwa kweKomidi Lekukhetsa ye-Artificial Intelligence.
Kulenyanga, i-DARPA imemetele kutsi itawutsatsa imali lengemadola latigidzigidzi letimbili kuloluhlelo lolubitwa ngekutsi yi-AI Next.
Mayelana ne-NSF, DARPA muva nje seyivele ifake imali lengetulu kwetigidzi temadola letilikhulu ngemnyaka ekucwaningeni nge-AI.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, umtsetfo waseMelika lobekafuna kusungulwa kweKhomishini Yekuvikeleka Kwavelonkhe yeTebungcweti beTekwenta awuzange ubonakale kutsi uyalandelwa etinyangeni letinyenti.
Bantfu baseMacedonia bavota ngekutsi bashintje libito lalelive labo
Bantfu baseMacedonia bavota ngeLisontfo kutsi bagucule libito lelive libe yi "Republic of North Macedonia", intfo letawucedza kungevani kwabo lokutsatse umnyaka loningi neGreece lebeyivimbele kujoyina i-EU kanye ne-NATO.
IGrisi, lenesifundza lesitsi iMacedonia, itsatsa libito lalelive lelingumakhelwane wayo wasenyakatfo njengelokuvuma kubusa indzawo yayo futsi seyiyivele ikuvimbele kutsi ijoyine i-NATO kanye ne-European Union.
Ngekuvumelana ngaJuni, bohulumende lababili bafinyelela esivumelwaneni mayelana neligama lelisha, kodvwa labaphikisi bemave ngemave batsi lolushintjo lutawubhubhisa buwena bebantfu labanyenti besive semaSlav aseMacedonia.
Umengameli George Ivanov utsi angeke avote kulolukhetfo futsi umkhankaso wekubukela phansi lolukhetfo ushiye kungabata kutsi lolukhetfo lutawuphumelela yini kufinyelela ku-50% walokubalulekile kute lolukhetfo lube semtsetfweni.
Umbuto lobhalwe ebhalothini utsi: Uyavuma yini kuba lilunga le-NATO kanye ne-EU ngekwemukela sivumelwano neGreece?
Basekeli baloku kuguculwa kwelibito, lokufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaev, batsi bekuyindleko lefanele kutsi ikhokhwe kute itfole imvume yekungena emalungeni lafana ne-EU kanye ne-NATO yeMacedonia, lelinye lemave latalwa ekubhujisweni kweYugoslavia.
"Ngifike lamuhla kute ngivote likusasa lelive lami, kute ngivote bantfu labasha baseMacedonia kute bakhone kuphila ngekukhululeka ngaphansi kwe-European Union ngobe kusho kuphila lokuphephile kitsi sonkhe", kusho Olivera Georgijevska, 79, eSkopje.
Nanobe kungakafaneli kutsi kube nemtsetfo, linani lelikhulu lemalunga ePhalamende latsi atawuhlonipha imiphumela yekuvota kute ente sincumo.
Kuguculwa kweligama kudzinga emavoti langulokubili kulokutsatfu ePhalamende.
LiKhomishani lekuKhetsa lavelonkhe litsi kute umbiko wekuhlukunyetwa kwemtsetfo kusukela nga-1:00 ntsambama.
Nanobe kunjalo, kubonakala kutsi emavoti afike ku-16%, nakucatsaniswa na-34% elukhetfweni lwendlu yelinyenti lwanga-2016 ngesikhatsi ema-66% alabo lababhalisile bakhipha emavoti abo.
"Ngilapha kute ngivote bantfwana bami, indzawo yetfu iseYurophu", kusho Gjose Tanevski, loneminyaka lengu-62, lowakhetsa enhloko-dolobha, Skopje.
INdvuna yeMbuso yaseMacedonia Zoran Zaev, umkakhe Zorica nendvodzana yakhe Dushko baniketa emavoti abo elukhetfweni lolukhulu eMacedonia loluhambisana nekuguculwa kwelibito lelive lelitawuvula indlela yelive kutsi lijoyine iNATO kanye ne-European Union eStrumica, eMacedonia, Septhemba 30, 2018.
Emuva kwephalamende eSkopje, Vladimir Kavardarkov, loneminyaka lengu-54, walungisa lihlaka lelincane futsi wahosha titulo takhe emathendeni labekabekwe ngulabo labebatawuvala lolukhetfo.
"Sivumile kujoyina iNATO ne-EU, kepha sifuna kujoyina ngenhlonipho, hhayi ngemnyango wetisebenti", kusho Kavadarkov.
Silive leliphuyile, kodvwa sinesithunzi.
Nangabe bangasifuni kutsi sibe ngemaMacedonia, singaya eChina naseRussia futsi sibe yincenye yekuhlanganiswa kwe-Euro-Asia.
Ndvunankhulu Zaev utsi kuba lilunga le-NATO kutawuletsa lutfo lolunyenti loludzingekako lwekutjala imali eMacedonia, lenekungasebenti lokungaba ngu-20%.
"Ngiyakholwa kutsi linyenti lebantfu litawusekela loku ngobe ngetulu kwa 80% webantfu bakitsi basekela i-EU ne-NATO", kusho Zaev ngemuva kwekuniketa emavoti akhe.
Watsi imiphumela yalolucwaningo itawucinisekisa likusasa letfu.
Umphumela weluphenyo lolushicilelwe yi-Macedonian Institute for Policy Research ngeMsombuluko, utsi emkhatsini wa-30 na-43% webantfu batawugucuka baye kulelovotelwa - lokusho kutsi basuke basuke basele kancane kunaloko lokudzingekako.
Lolunye luhlolo lolwentiwa siteshi se-TV i-Telma Macedonia, lwatfola kutsi bantfu labangu-57% bahlela kuvota ngeLisontfo.
