Eminyakeni lecishe ibe siphohlongo ngililunga lePhalamende yeTemisebenti, umhlangano weKomidi leMphakatsi ngaLesihlanu kusihlwa bewunguloku nje.
Ngalokubuhlungu lamuhla, simo semihlangano leminyenti netetsembiso tepolitiki "lencono, lenemusa" asikaze sikhunjulwe, uma ngabe, vele, sacala.
Kwehlukana kwemibono ngekhatsi kwelicembu lebasebenti bekukhula kakhulu futsi kute kubeketelelana futsi yonkhe imibono beyibukwa ngemandla.
Loku kwacala ngekushesha nje Jeremy nakangenela bukhosi, njengobe bekangumngani lebengicinga kutsi angahlanganyela naye imibono lefanako kutepolitiki, wacala kungilindzela kutsi ngishintje futsi ngitsatse sikhundla lebengingeke ngisitsatse - kungaba sekuvikeleni sive noma emakethe lehlangene ye-EU.
Ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi nangikhuluma embikwebantfu - futsi akukhatsaleki kutsi ngitsini - kulandzela kungcola lokukhulu kuma social media lokucela kutsi kukhetfwe, kugxeka ipolitiki lesemkhatsini, kungitjela kutsi angifanele kutsi ngibe lilunga le Labour.
Angisiye yedvwa lohlangabetana naloku.
Kuliciniso kutsi ngiyati kutsi nginenhlanhla kunebangani bami ngobe imibono lebeyibhekiswe kimi beyichubekela etintfweni tepolitiki.
Ngiyamangaliswa buchwepheshe kanye nekulinganiselwa kwalabangani bami lababhekana nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi nobe kubandlululwa onkhe malanga kodvwa bangaphunyuki.
Lenye yetintfo letidvumatako kuletikhatsi tepolitiki kutsi lizinga lekusetjentiswa kabi kwemalungelo eluntfu livame kakhulu.
Jeremy Corbyn watsi kuleliviki leliphelile, licembu lebasebenti kumele lisite ekwakheni lisiko lekubeketelela.
Liciniso likutsi asisesiyo inkholo lenkhulu futsi ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi, yonkhe imitsetfo yekungaletsembi nobe kugucula imitsetfo yemaphathi itawuba yincenye lencane.
Ngitfole teluleko letinyenti kuleminyaka lemibili leyengcile letangikhutsata kutsi ngihlale phansi, ngingabi nemibono leminyenti, bese ngitsi "kulungile".
Kodvwa angizange ngingenele tepolitiki kute ngente njalo.
Kusukela ngajoyina licembu le-Labour eminyakeni lengu-32 leyengcile ngisesemfundvweni, ngikhutsatwa kukhatsateka kwahulumende waThatcher lokwabangela kutsi likilasi lami lesikolwa leliphelele liwe, bengisolo ngilwa ngemsebenti lomuhle wemmango kulabo labadzinga kakhulu - njengemsiti wasekhaya kanye nelisekela lesigungu sahulumende.
Angizange ngifihle kutsi ngenta tintfo tepolitiki, ngisho nangesikhatsi sekukhetfwa kwami.
Kute umuntfu eNottingham leseMpumalanga lotawubese uyabuta kutsi ngitiphi timiso tami kanye netintfo lengingavumelani nato ekuholeni kwanyalo.
Kulabo labetfula ticelo ngeLesihlanu, lengingakusho kutsi njengobe lelive lihamba ngekushesha liye ekuhlukaniseni bukhosi, loku kutawulimata ibhizinisi yelive letfu kanye nemisebenti yemphakatsi, angifuni kuchitsa sikhatsi sami nemandla ami ngekwetsembeka kubaholi be-Labour.
Kodvwa-ke, umlayeto wami awusiwo weNottingham Momentum, kepha ngiwo lowabakhetfwa bami, njengelilunga le-Labour nobe cha, ngiyajabula kukhonta nine futsi ngiyetsembisa kutsi kute kusongelwa kwekukhishwa esikhundleni nobe luhlelo lwetembusave lolungangivimbela kutsi ngente lengikholwa kutsi kutawuba lusito kini nonkhe.
