Umdlalo wa Grant Anderson ngemzuzu we-14, lowaguculwa ngu Frazier Climo, wafaka Ayr embili, kepha likhadi lelimtfubi lelikhokhelwe indvuna yase Scotland Rory Hughes, laniketwa kulo mdlalo ngema Warriors, lanika Melrose litfuba lekufaka inombolo futsi Jason Baggot wafaka umdlalo longakaguculwa.
