Bakhi be-Valentino na-Thom Browne bakhipha tinhloko letinkhulu te-SS19 yabo ngesikhatsi bacala umbukiso wabo we-Paris Fashion Week.
Letigcoko letingasebenti kahle tivele tihlasele i-Instagram ehlobo futsi labadvwebi bavele bakhombisa tintfo tabo letitsite letibukekako.
Intfo leyenta Valentino abonakale kutsi unesitayela semakhrimune lesinemaphethini lamakhulu lahlanganisa inhloko yakhe.
Tintfo letinkhulu lebetitfolakala tifaka ekhatsi ema-melon lahlotjiswe ngemadayimane, umchele wemilingo ngisho neliphayinaphu, kodvwa bekungasito tintfo lebetentelwe kufutfumelisa inhloko.
Thom Browne waphindze wakhombisa inhlanganisela yetimphahla tekugcoka letingajwayelekile - futsi ngesikhatsi lesitsite ngaphambi kwe-Halloween.
Tintfo letinyenti temaski letinemibala leyehlukene, letihlotjiswe ngetindzebe letinjengetaHannibal Lecter kunetintfo te haute couture.
Lenye ifana netintfo tekuntjweza letihlome ngemanti, inemabhande kanye netingilazi, kantsi lenye ifana nelitfonsi lelikhanyako.
Nangabe uchubeka nekubuka letintfo letinkhulu kangaka - bese uyajabula.
Bantfu labatsandza kudvweba bacabanga kutsi letindvwangu letinkhulu titawutfunyelwa emgwacweni lomkhulu losedvute nawe.
Tibhavu letinkhulu betitintfo letitsengiswa kakhulu eLa Bomba, letingubo tetjani letinetinyawo letimbili letindze letisetjentiswa ngubo bonkhe bantfu lokufaka ekhatsi Rihanna kuya ku Emily Ratajkowski.
Kukhonta emalebuli ngemuva kwetigcoko kungasebenti kahle, futsi kusebentisa imisakato yetenhlalo kwenta kutsi kube netintfo letinkhulu letisetjentiswako etindzaweni tekuhamba - emabhokisi emanti lacishe afane netimphahla tekugcoka - latigcokwa ngemamodeli lanetimphahla letincane.
