John Edward: Lwati lwetilwimi lubaluleke kakhulu kubantfu labahlala emhlabeni wonkhe.
Tikolwa tasemakhaya taseScotland tigcina umlandvo wekuhlonishwa ngekwemfundvo, futsi loku kwachubeka nga-2018 ngemiphumela lemihle kakhulu, leyakhiwa ngumfundzi ngamunye kanye nemphumelelo lehlangene kutemidlalo, tebuciko, temculo kanye nekusebenta kamatima.
Ngetikolwa letingetulu kwa-30 000 eScotland, letikolwa, letimelelwa Sigungu Setikolwa Lesimele SaseScotland (SCIS) tenta konkhe lokusemandleni ato kute tinikete bafundzi nebatali babo lusito lolukhulu.
Tikolwa letitimele tihlose kulungisa bafundzi bato kute batfole imfundvo lechubekako naletsi: imfundvo lephakeme, umsebenti wabo, kanye nendzima yabo njengebahlali bemhlaba.
Njengobe luhlangotsi lwetemfundvo lungakwati kwakha nekusebentisa luhlelo lwetemfundvo lwetemfundvo ngendlela lefunwa ngulabanye, sibona tilwimi tesimanje tichubeka nekuba tifundvo letitsandvwa kakhulu futsi letifunwa tikolweni letinyenti.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, loko lokushoko kutawungena engcondvweni yakhe.
Nakukhuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko lokushoko kutawufika enhlitiyweni yakhe".
Loku kusikhumbuta kutsi singeke setsembele esiNgisini kuphela nangabe sifuna kwakha budlelwane nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Ngekuya ngemiphumela yemnyaka, sibona kutsi lulwimi lutawutfola indzawo lencono kakhulu ekuphumeleleni etikolweni letitimele.
Bonkhe bafundzi labangu-68% labafundza tilwimi bangena ku-A Plus.
Lemininingwane, lehlanganiswe etikolweni letingu-74 letiyincenye ye-SCIS ikhombisa kutsi 72% webafundzi batfola ema-A Plus ngesiMandarin, kantsi 72% walabo labafundza siJalimane, 69% walabo labafundza siFulentji, kanye na-63% walabo labafundza siSpanish nabo batfola ema-A.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letitimele eScotland tisekela tilwimi tangaphandle njengelwati lolubalulekile lolutawufuneka kubantfwana nakubantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Namuhla tilwimi, njengetinhlobo tetihloko, tibekwe ezingeni lelifanako netihloko te-STEM (Isayensi, bucwepheshe, bungcweti kanye netibalo) eluhlelweni lwetemfundvo lwesimanje nakuletinye tindzawo.
Lucwaningo lolwentiwa yi-UK Department for Employment and Skills nga-2014 lwatfola kutsi etintfweni letinyenti letibangela bacashi kutsi balwe kamatima kute bagcwalise tikhala, liphesenti le-17 libangelwa kutsi bantfu bete emakhono elulwimi.
Ngako-ke, emakhono elulwimi ayagcugcutelwa kute kulungiselelwe bantfu labasha umsebenti wekutiphilisa.
Njengobe kunetisebenti letinyenti letifuna emakhono elulwimi, lamakhono abaluleke kakhulu emhlabeni lowetayelekile.
Nobe ngabe ngumuphi umsebenti umuntfu lawukhetsako, nangabe sebafundze lulwimi lwesibili, batawuzuza kakhulu ngekutfola emakhono latawuhlala aphila.
Kukwati kuchumana nebantfu bakulamanye emave ngalokucondzile kutawenta umuntfu lokhuluma tilwimi letinyenti abe nguloyo lotawuncintisana naye.
Ngekusho kweluphenyo lwe-YouGov lwebantfu labadzala baseBrithani labangetulu kwa-4 000 nga-2013, emaphesenti langu-75 abo abakhulumi lulwimi lolungakalungi kahle kute bakwati kucoca futsi siFulentji silulwimi kuphela lolukhulunywa etinhlotjeni letinemadijithi lamabili, lokungu-15%.
Kungako kutsenga ekufundziseni tilwimi kubantfwana bakamuva kubaluleke kakhulu.
Kuba nemakhono elulwimi lolunyenti, ikakhulukati emaveni latfutfukako, kutawuniketa bantfwana ematfuba lamanyenti ekutfola umsebenti lonenjongo.
E-Scotland, tonkhe tikolwa titawufundzisa tilwimi letehlukene.
Letinye tikolwa titawucala kufundzisa tilwimi tesimanje, letinye tifundzise tilwimi letitawuba yimcoka kakhulu eNgilandi kuleminyaka letako, njengaleti tase-Mandarin nobe taseJapan.
Nobe ngabe ngumiphi imikhuba umntfwana wakho lafuna kuyenta, kutawuhlala kunetilwimi letinyenti longatikhetsa esikolweni lesitsite, lesinabo bothishela labati kahle.
Tikolwa letitimele taseScotland tinenhloso yekuniketa imvelo yekufundza letawulungiselela bantfwana futsi ibaphe emakhono ladzingekile kute baphumelele, nome ngabe kwentekani esikhatsini lesitako.
Akungabateki kutsi lamuhla, esimeni sebhizinisi lesihlanganisiwe, lulwimi lutawuhlala luyincenye lebalulekile yekubaluleka kwelive, ngako-ke loku kumele kubonakale emfundvweni.
Ecinisweni, lulwimi lwanamuhla kufanele lubhekwe "njengelwati lwekukhulumisana nemave emhlaba".
Tikolwa letitimele titawuchubeka nekuniketa lendlela yekukhetsa, kwehlukahlukana kanye nekunconola bantfu labasha baseScotland.
Il faut bien le faire. Kufanele kube kahle.
John Edward unguMcondzisi weSikolo saseScotland Lesimele
