Kulindzela kwebantfu kutsi babone LeBron James enta licala lakhe lekucala e-Los Angeles Lakers sekuphelile.
Umceceshi weLakers, Luke Walton, umemetele kutsi James utawudlala ekucaleni kwemdlalo we-pre-season ngeLisontfo ku-Denver Nuggets eSan Diego.
Nanobe kunjalo, akukabonakali kutsi utawudlala emaminitsi lamangaki.
"Kutawuba ngetulu kwalokunye futsi kungaphansi kwa-48", kusho Walton kuwebhusayithi yeLakers.
Umlandzi weLakers Mike Trudell watfumela umlayeto kuTwitter watsi James utawudlala emaminitsi lambalwa.
Ngemuva kwekuceceshwa ekucaleni kwaleliviki, James wabutwa ngeluhlelo lwakhe lwekudlala imidlalo lesitfupha ye-Lakers.
"Kulesigaba semsebenti wami, angidzingi kudlala imidlalo yasesikhatsini lesengcile kute ngilungele", washo njalo.
Luhlelo Lwemhlangano WaboMengameli Trump EWest Virginia, YouTube
Mengameli Donald Trump uvule umhlangano wekukhankasa ebusuku eWheeling, eWest Virginia.
Lena yimibutsano yekucala yaTrump yetinkhulumo letisihlanu letihlelelwe liviki lelitako, kufaka ekhatsi kumisa etindzaweni letijabulisako letifaka ekhatsi iTennessee neMississippi.
Ngemuva kwekucinisekisa kutsi livoti lihlehlisiwe kute akhone kukhetsa umuntfu lotawugcwalisa sikhundla sakhe seNkantolo lePhakeme, Trump uhlose kwakha kwesekelwa kwakhe elukhetfweni lolutako lwesikhatsi lesisemkhatsini ngobe emaRephabliki abeka engotini yekulahlekelwa ligunya lekusebentisa iCongress uma ngabe kuvota kwentiwa ngaNovemba.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi semhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia kusihlwa futsi ungabukela njani ku-inthanethi?
Umhlangano waMengameli Trump eWheeling, eWest Virginia, uhlelelwe 7:00 ebusuku, kusihlwa, ngeMgcibelo, September 29, 2018.
Ungayibuka imihlangano yaTrump eWest Virginia ku-inthanethi ngekusakaza bukhoma ku-YouTube.
Kubonakala shengatsi Trump utawucoca ngekulalelwa kwelicala laMengameli lotawukhetfwa ngu Brett Kavanaugh, lobekacansulwa kakhulu ngemuva kwekubekwa licala lekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicasi futsi lokwabonakala kutsi livoti lelinguSenate litawubanjwa liviki linye ngesikhatsi i-FBI iliphenya.
Kodvwa inhloso lenkhulu yaloluhlelo lwekuhlangana kusita emaRephabliki kutsi atfole emandla ekubukana nelukhetfo lwaNovemba.
Ngako-ke, umkhankhaso waMengameli Trump utsi imihlangano lesihlanu kuleliviki lelitako ihlose "kucinisa emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli njengoba emaRephabliki etama kuvikela nekukhulisa linyenti lawo eSenate naseNdlini yeTiphatsimandla", ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
"Kulawula iCongress kubaluleke kakhulu eluhlelweni lwakhe kutsi Mengameli utawuhamba ahambe ahambe emaveni lamanyenti njengobe silwa nesikhatsi sekukhankasa", kusho sikhulumi semkhankhaso waTrump lesingafuni kubitwa ngeligama sitjela iReuters.
Lokuhlelelwe eWesbanco Arena eWheeling, lomhlangano wakusihlwa kulindzeleke kutsi ufake bafaka sandla base "Ohio nase Pennsylvania kanye nekubamba lichaza kwetindzaba tase Pittsburgh", ngekusho kwe West Virginia Metro News.
NgaMgcibelo kutawuba luhambo lwesibili lwaTrump eWest Virginia enyangeni leyendlulile, live lalincoba ngetiphakamiso letingetulu kwa-40 nga-2016.
Trump wetama kusita Patrick Morrisey, umcashi waseWest Virginia lofuna kuba ngumengameli weSigungu seSigungu seMhlaba (i-Republican) lowehluleka kakhulu kutfola imiphumela.
"Akusiko kuhle kutsi Morrisey afike abe ngumengameli kute atfutfukise indlela yakhe yekukhetsa", kusho Simon Haeder, losati setembusave eNyuvesi yase West Virginia, ngekusho kwe Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Licembu laseMelika libonisa sibindzi sekugcina litsemba lalo emdlalweni weLisontfo
Ngemuva kwetinsita letintsatfu telicembu linye, umhlangano welicembu letine ngeMgcibelo ntsambama ngulona loludzingekako kule-Ryder Cup.
I-swing yemandla ingumcondvo wemidlalo lekhishwe ngulabadlali, futsi kute lokwendlula kulomdlalo.
Bacabanga kutsi sinjani simo nyalo?
"Bekukadze kuhola emaphuzu lasitfupha futsi nyalo sekuphetse emaphoyinti lamane, ngako-ke ngicabanga kutsi sicabanga kutsi kuncane lokwentekile", kwasho Jordan Spieth njengobe ahamba ngalelo langa.
EYurophu kunenzuzo lenkhulu ngobe inemaphuzu lamane ekuhola ngemidlalo lengu-12 lesele.
Kodvwa licembu laseMelika, njengobe Spieth asho, belicabanga kutsi lincane kakhulu likhono futsi linetintfo letinyenti letingaba yintsandvo, hhayi ngaphandle kwelicembu laSpieth naJustin Thomas labadlala ndzawonye lilanga lonkhe futsi ngamunye wabo wafaka emaphoyinti lamatsatfu kulamane.
Spieth wadlala ngendlela lebulalako kusuka endzaweni yekubhala kuya endzaweni yekuhlanyela futsi wahola ngendlela lebonakalako.
Umkhosi wekubonga wacala ngesikhatsi sekufika sikhatsi sakhe, wenta umcibisholo lobalulekile wekwenta umdlalo ube ngulobuhambisana naye ngesikhatsi yena naThomas sebalahlekelwe ngu-2-2.
Umdlalo wakhe wekubetsela phansi ku-15 wabonwa ngemsindvo lofanako, umsindvo lowatisa kutsi bekatsemba kutsi iMelika angeke ilahlekelwe.
"Kufanele wetame kamatima futsi ukhatsateke ngemdlalo wakho", kusho Spieth.
Bonkhe labadlali sebahambe nyalo.
18 wemigodzi lekumele ibekwe luphawu.
Labadlali labadlale emalanga lamabili ekucala labanemaphuzu lamanyenti kunaSpieth naThomas nguFrancesco Molinari naTommy Fleetwood, tinganekwane letingenakuphikiswa teRyder Cup.
Labashadisi baseYurophu labangafani kodvwa labatsandzekako banebantfu labane futsi bangenta emaphutsa.
"Moliwood" nguyona ncenye yelicembu lelingakashayi bogey ngeMgcibelo ntsambama, kepha baphindze bagweme bogey ngeMgcibelo ekuseni, ngeLesihlanu ntsambama kanye ne back nine ngeLesihlanu ekuseni.
Lolujubo, nendlela emandla abo labekageleta ngayo kuyo nakulesicuku lebesicindzetelekile, kwabenta baba nesiciniseko sekutsi bangulabadlali labatawubanjwa ngeLisontfo, futsi kute lomunye lodvumile kunaFleetwood nobe Molinari lotawubamba emandla ekuwina eYurophu ngesikhatsi lilanga lishona eLe Golf National.
Kuncono kutsi tibekwe emaceleni lahlukene ngesikhatsi sinye.
Nobe kunjalo, kusesekusenesikhatsi kutsi sikhulume ngekuncoba kweYurophu.
Bubba Watson na Webb Simpson bacedza umsebenti waSergio Garcia, ingwazi ye-fourball ekuseni, ngesikhatsi ahlanganiswa na-Alex Noren.
Lenye bogey kanye naleminye lemibili kulesisishiyagalolunye sekucala kufana nekumba umgodzi longeke ukhuphulwe ngulabadlali beligalufa baseSpain kanye nebaseSweden.
Nanobe kunjalo, kute umuntfu longakusita kutsi uphume kulomgodzi ngeLisontfo.
I-Fourball ne-Foursome yintfo lenhle kakhulu longayibuka ngoba kuyintfo lechubekako emkhatsini webalingani, seluleko labasinikako, seluleko labangasiniki nekutsi indlela yekusebenta ingashintja njani ngekushesha.
Kuze kube ngunyalo, emave aseYurophu abedlala kahle kakhulu njengemacembu futsi abehola kakhulu ekucaleni kwelusuku lwekugcina, kepha luhlelo lwemacembu lamane nalo lukhombisa kutsi licembu laseMelika linesibindzi sekulwa nanobe labanye bantfu bangababuta, ikakhulukati eMelika.
I-Europe ihola 10-6 ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup
I-Europe itawusebentisa litfuba lelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwekuphakama emdlalweni we-fourball ne-foursome ngaMgcibelo ngekuhola nga-10-6 kunemave aseMelika.
Labashayi bemidlalo lababili labakhutsatako Tommy Fleetwood na Francesco Molinari bahola ngemahloni lamabili kunebantfu lababili labalwe ngu Tiger Woods lowalwela kufinyelela emaphuzu abo kuze kube ngunyalo eLe Golf National ngemaphuzu lamane.
I-European Thomas Bjorn, lebeyifuna kugcina indondo lebeyingayitfoli eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile eHazeltine, yancoba licembu laseMelika lebelibekwe emaphutsa kulentfwasahlobo, yawenta waba 3-1.
I-United States iniketa imphikiswano lenkhulu kuma-foursome, incobe imidlalo lemibili, kepha ayikwati kunciphisa umncane.
Licembu laJim Furyk lidzinga emaphuzu lasiphohlongo emidlalweni lengu-12 ngeLisontfo kute livikele umchele walo.
Fleetwood waba wekucala eYurophu kutsi atfole emaphuzu lamane lalandzelanako, kantsi yena naMolinari, lowatfola ligama lelitsi "Molliwood" ngemuva kwelusuku lwekugcina, baba yincenye yesibili yetinhlobo tebantfu labatfole emaphuzu lamane ekuvula imidlalo yabo lemine emlandvweni weRyder Cup.
Ngemuva kwekuncoba Woods na Patrick Reed ku-fourball baba nesisindvo sekuncoba Woods lowagwaza kanye ne-American debutant Bryson Dechambeau ngekucinisa 5&4.
Woods, lowatikhandza asebenta emidlalweni lemibili ngaMgcibelo, bekakhombisa buhle ngalesinye sikhatsi kepha ulahlekelwe yimidlalo lengu-19 kulemashumi lamabili nemfica emidlalweni lemine yelibhola letinyawo kanye nelibhola letinyawo letine kanye nemidlalo lesikhombisa lelandzelanako.
Justin Rose, waphumula ekuseni ku-fourball, wase ubuyela emuva wahlangana na Henrik Stenson ku-foursome futsi walahlekelwa 2&1 ku-Dustin Johnson na Brooks Koepka - labangu-1 na-3 emhlabeni.
Europe ayizange ikhone kufinyelela kuyo ngisho nobe bekunemalanga lamahle futsi kunemoya eningizimu-nshonalanga yeParis.
Labancobe emahlandla lamatsatfu Jordan Spieth naJustin Thomas baletsa umfutfo wemaMelika ngemaphuzu lamabili ngeMgcibelo.
Batfola kuncoba lokumangalisako lokungu 2&1 ku Jon Rahm na Ian Poulter base Spain ku fourball base babuya futsi kute bancobe Poulter na Rory McIlroy 4&3 ku foursome ngemuva kwekulahlekelwa yimigodzi lemibili yekucala.
Kwenteka kabili emlandvweni we Ryder Cup kutsi licembu libuye lisuka ekulahlekelweni ngemaphuzu lamane lingene emdlalweni munye, nanobe njengaloyo lowalwela umchudzelwano licembu le Furyk belidinga kuphela emaphuzu ekudlala kute livikele umchele.
Nanobe kunjalo, ngemuva kwekuba ngulababili labahle kakhulu emalanga lamabili, kuhlasela kwaLisontfo bekubonakala shengatsi kutawubacedza emandla.
INyakatfo Korea itsi 'ayikhoni' kucedza tikhali tayo ngaphandle kwekwetsembana
NgaMgcibelo, iNdvuna yeTangaphandle yaseNyakatfo Korea yatjela i-UN ngetindlela tekucindzetela letichubekisa phambili nekungetsembi iMelika nekutsi angeke ikhone kucedza tikhali tayo te-nuclear ngalokungakhetsi esimeni lesinjalo.
Ri Yong Ho watjela umhlangano wemnyaka we-World Nuclear Organization General Assembly kutsi iNyakatfo Korea yente "tinyatselo letibalulekile letibonisa inhloso lenhle" kulomnyaka lophelile, njengekumisa kuhlolwa kwenyukliya nemakhemikhali, kucedza indzawo yekuhlola inyukliya, kanye nekwetsembisa kungabi netikhali temandla enyukliya kanye nebuchwepheshe.
"Noko, asiboni kutsi kunemphendvulo lefanelekile levela eMelika", washo njalo.
"Ngaphandle kwekwetsembela eMelika ngeke sibe nekwetsemba kuvikeleka kwetfu kwesive futsi esimeni lesinjalo angeke sikhone kutilahla tikhali tetfu ngekushesha".
Ngesikhatsi Ri aphindze akhonona ngalendlela lefanako yase North Korea mayelana nekumelana kwe Washington ngendlela "lehlelekile" yekulwa nekususa inyukliya lapho khona iNorth Korea itawujeziswa ngekutitsatsela tinyatselo letihlelekile, washo emavi labalulekile ekutsi ayiphikisani ngalokuphelele njengobe kwentiwe yiPyongyang esikhatsini lesengcile.
Ri abhekise esitatimendeni lesihlangene lesikhishwe nguKim Jong Un na Donald Trump emhlanganweni wabohulumende baseMelika wekucala kanye nebaholi baseNorth Korea eSingapore ngaJuni 12, ngesikhatsi Kim etsembisa kutfutfukisa "kuvalwa kwenyukliya enhlonhlweni yaseKorea" kantsi Trump wetsembisa kucinisekisa kuphepha kweNorth Korea.
INyakatfo Korea beyifuna kuphela kweMphi yaseKorea yanga-1950-53 ngalokusemtsetfweni, kepha iMelika yatsi iPyongyang kufanele ivale tikhali tayo te-nuclear kucala.
I-Washington iphindze yala kucela kwehlukunyetwa kwetigwebo letinkhulu temave emhlaba etikweNyakatfo Korea.
"I-United States icinile 'ekucedzeni i-denuclearization' futsi yenta ncono kucindzeteleka ngekubeka tigwebo letingaba yintfo ledzinga kutsi ifinyelele imigomo yayo ngekucindzetelwa, futsi iphindze incobe 'kucedza imphi'", kusho Ri.
"Lomcondvo wekutsi kujeziswa kungasenta sigcine sesikhotsama, ngumkhuba webantfu labangati tsine.
Kodvwa inkinga kutsi kuhlale kunetigwebo kutawujulisa kungetsembi kwetfu".
Ri akazange akhulume ngeluhlelo lwekuhlangana kwesibili emkhatsini waKim naTrump lokwavetwa baholi baseMelika e-United Nations ekucaleni kwaleliviki.
Kunaloko, lomengameli wagcizelela imihlangano lemitsatfu emkhatsini waKim neMholi waseNingizimu Korea Moon Jae-in etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, futsi wachubeka watsi: "Nangabe inkinga yekulwa nekucitfwa kwembutfo welitulu ivela eSouth Korea hhayi eMelika, i-denuclearization yesichingi saseKorea angeke ihlangane naloluhlobo lwekucitfwa kwembutfo welitulu".
Nanobe kunjalo, inchazelo yalenkhulumo yaRi yehluke kakhulu kunaloko lokwenteka emnyakeni lowengcile, ngesikhatsi akhuluma e-UN General Assembly kutsi kuhlasela i-North Korea ngemakhemikhali emhlabatsini waseMelika bekungeke kuphele ngemuva kwekutsi "Mnu Mnu Mnuz Satan" Trump abite Kim ngekutsi "ngumuntfu wemakhemikhali" emkhankasweni wekutivikela.
Kulomnyaka emhlanganweni we-UN, Trump lowatsi emnyakeni lowengcile wafuna "kubhubhisa" iNyakatfo Korea ngalokuphelele, wadvumisa Kim ngekutsatsa sinyatselo sekuhlukunyetwa, kodvwa lomsebenti lomkhulu usasele kutsi wentiwe futsi netigwebo kumele tihlale tibekekile kuze kube ngulapho iNyakatfo Korea seyiyekele kukhipha emabutfo ayo enyukliya.
NgaLesitsatfu, Trump watsi akanaso sikhatsi saloku, "Nangabe kutsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu - akunandzaba", washo.
I-China neRussia batsi uMkhandlu Wekuvikeleka Wemave Emhlaba (i-UN Security Council) kumele ujezise iPyongyang ngaloluhambo lwayo.
Nanobe kunjalo, iNdvuna yeMbuso yaseMelika, Mike Pompeo, watjela uMkhandlu Wekuvikeleka weNhlangano Yemave Emhlaba ngeLesine kutsi: "Kucinisekisa kutsi kucinisekiswa kwetincumo teMkhandlu Wekuvikeleka kumele kuchubeke ngekuciniseka futsi akukafaneli kwehluleke size sati kutsi kucedvwa kwenyukliya kuphelele, futsi kuyaphelelwa".
UMkhandlu Wetekuphepha waVelonkhe wavumelana ngekwenyusa tinhlawulo tekucindzetelwa kweNyakatfo Korea kusukela nga-2006 ngemitamo yekumisa imali ye-Pyongyang yetintfo tayo te-nuclear kanye netinhlelo tayo te-ballistic missile.
Pompeo wahlangana naRi eceleni kwe-UN General Assembly wase utsi utawuphindze avakashele iPyongyang kulenyanga letako kute alungiselele umhlangano wesibili.
Pompeo uvakashele eNyakatfo Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kodvwa luhambo lwakhe lwekugcina aluhambanga kahle.
Washiya iPyongyang ngaJulayi atsi kukhona lokwentiwako, kepha iNorth Korea ngekhatsi kwema-awa yatsi "unemibono lefanana neyeligenge".
I-North Korea yetsembisa emhlanganweni wayo na Moon kulenyanga kutsi itawuvala tindzawo tayo temakhemikhali kanye netakhiwo tayo temakhemikhali uma iMelika itsatsa "tinyatselo letifanele".
Watsi Kim wamtjela kutsi "atsatse sinyatselo lesihambisana" netifiso takhe, lokuyintfo lebeyitsenjiswa nguTrump eSingapore kanye nekuhamba ngendlela yekwenta budlelwane bube busetulu neWashington.
Bafundzi baseHarvard batsatsa tifundvo tekuphumula ngalokwenele
Sifundvo lesisha eHarvard University kulomnyaka sitsi bonkhe bafundzi belibanga lekucala balale sikhatsi lesengetiwe, kute balwisane nemasiko ekufundza ngekutsandza bantfu labadvuna labakhutsata i-caffeine.
Lomunye umfundzi utfole kutsi bafundzi labasemanyuvesi laphakeme kakhulu emhlabeni bavame kungawati umcondvo wekutivikela.
Charles Czeisler, longuprofesa wetemphilo yekulala eHarvard Medical School futsi lowati kabanti ngeBrigham and Women's Hospital, wakha sifundvo, lacabanga kutsi bekucala ngca eMelika.
Wasungulwa ngemuva kwekukhuluma ngemiphumela yekungalali kahle ekufundzeni.
'Kwatsi ekugcineni kwefika intfombatana kimi yatsi: 'Kungani kungitjela nyalo, emnyakeni wami wekugcina?'
Lomntfwana utsi kute umuntfu longitjela ngekubaluleka kwekulala - lokwangimangalisa,' asho kuThe Telegraph.
Lolu luhlelo lwekucala lolwasungulwa kulomnyaka, luchaza bafundzi ngekubaluleka kwekulala kahle lokwenta kutsi baphumelele etifundvweni nasemitameni yabo yekudlala futsi kutfutfukisa nenhlalakahle yabo.
Paul Barreira, longulomunye wabophrofesa betemphilo yengcondvo eHarvard Medical School futsi longumcondzisi wetemphilo enyuvesi, utsi inyuvesi yancuma kusungula loluhlelo ngemuva kwekubona kutsi bafundzi bebabete butfongo lobanele liviki lonkhe.
Letifundvo teli-awa linye tifaka ekhatsi luchungechunge lwemisebenti lechubekako.
Kulenye yetinhlelo bekunetibonwa tasendlini yekuhlala, lapho bafundzi bebabhala khona ngetinkomishi temakhofi, emakhethini, emabhulukwe etemidlalo kanye netincwadzi kute batfole inchazelo ngemiphumela ye-caffeine nekukhanya, nekutsi imiphumela yetemidlalo itsintfwa njani kungalali kahle, kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala sikhatsi lesanele.
Kulenye incenye, babambiqhaza bafundziswa kutsi kungakanani sikhatsi sekulala lokungaba yingoti ekuguleni kwenhlitiyo, sifo sekushaya unyawo, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Lemephu yasekolishi, lenetitfombe letihambisanako, bese ikhutsata bafundzi kutsi bacabange ngemphilo yabo yamalanga onkhe.
'Sati kutsi loku angeke kusishintje simo sebantfwana ngekushesha.
Kodvwa siyakholelwa kutsi banelilungelo lekwati - njengobe nawe unelilungelo lekwati ngemiphumela yekukhetsa kubhema,' kwengeta Profesa Czeisler.
Watsi lisiko lekutigabatisa 'ngekusebenta ebusuku' lisekhona, futsi ubuye atsi bucwepheshe lobusandza kwentiwa kanye nekucindzetelwa lokunyenti kwebafundzi kutsi bangakhoni kulala kahle kuyinkinga lekhulako.
Kutfola butfongo lobanele, lobunemphilo, kufanele kube 'sikhwama lesiyimfihlo' sekulwa nekucindzeteleka, kukhatsateka kanye nekukhatsateka, utsi - ngisho nekugwema kukhuluphala, ngobe kungalali kahle kwenta ingcondvo ivule indlela yekudla, lokuyintfo leyenta umuntfu ahlale alambile.
Raymond So, umntfwana waseCalifornia loneminyaka lengu-19 budzala lofundza ikhemistri kanye netintfo letiphilako letisita Phrofesa Czeisler kutsi akhe loluhlelo, watsatsa sinye setimfundvo takhe emnyakeni wakhe wekucala eHarvard.
Utsi leliklasi lamvulela emehlo futsi lamkhutsata kutsi ahlele tifundvo tasekolishi lonkhe.
Sinyatselo sakhe lesilandzelako, bekukutsi afune kutsi bonkhe bafundzi labaphotfule emabanga laphakeme bafundziswe kutsi bacedze luhlelo lolufanako lwekufundza ngaphambi kwekutsi bajoyine tikhungo letincintisanako.
Prof Czeisler utjela bafundzi kutsi bacabange kusebentisa ema-alamu ekulala, kanye nema-alamu ekuvuka, futsi bati ngemiphumela 'yekukhanya lokulibala lokulibala' lokukhishwa tibuko te-elekthroniki netibane te-LED, lokungahle kuphatamise umtimba wakho futsi kuholele etinkingeni tekulala.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Umgomo Wehla Umdlandla Webutfo LaGerrard
Kuphindze futsi, ema Rangers ativa buhlungu ngelilanga lekuhamba ngesikhatsi umshaya wa Dolly Menga uletsa licembu la Steven Gerrard lelahlekelwe ngu 1-0 eLivingston.
I-Ibrox yetama kutfola imphumelelo yekucala endleleni yabo, kusukela ngekuncoba kwabo 4-1 ngaFebruwari eSt Johnstone, kepha licembu laGary Holt lisandza kuniketa Gerrard kuncoba kwesibili emidlalweni lengu-18 njengemphhatsi, lokwenta kutsi lihambe ngemaphuzu lasiphohlongo ngemuva kwe Ladbrokes Premiership Hearts.
Meng wahlasela ngemizuzu lesikhombisa ngaphambi kwekuphela kwemzuzu wekucala futsi badlali beRangers lebebaphelelwe yingcondvo abazange babonakale kutsi bayalinganisa.
Ngesikhatsi ema Rangers asalele endzaweni yesitfupha, Livingston wenyukela endzaweni yesitsatfu, ngemuva nje kwemagoli eHibernian.
Kungenteka kube netinkinga letengetiwe ebaleni lemaRanger ngemuva kwekutsi umgcini welineni Calum Spence alashwe ngenca yekulimala enhloko ngemuva kwekujikijelwa intfo letsite.
Gerrard wenta tingucuko letisiphohlongo kulelicembu lelahlula i-Ayr kuya kumdlalo wekugcina weBetfred Cup.
Esikhundleni saloko, Holt uhamba naLiv 11 lowatfola yinye inombolo kumaHearts ngeliviki leliphelile futsi utawujabula ngekumangaza titsa takhe ngawo onkhe ematfuba.
Ema Rangers kungenteka kutsi abusa ngekubamba ibhola, kepha Livingston wasebentisa kahle ibhola lebebanayo.
Bekufanele kutsi bacedze ngekubhala phansi ngemuva kwemizuzu lemibili ngesikhatsi kudlalwa kwekucala lokuncane lokwafakwa nguScott Pittman ngekhatsi kwa-Allan McGregor, kepha umgadli welicembu wavulela ematfuba lamakhulu kakhulu.
