Umsunguli weGeiger counter
Nyalo, kusuka ekhasini le-Sunday Morning Almanac yetfu: September 30, 1882, eminyakeni lengu-136 leyendlulile, futsi itawuchubeka ikhule, lilanga lapho khona Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger, umuntfu lotawubitwa ngekutsi ngumuntfu lobonakalako, watalwa eJalimane.
Geiger wasungula indlela yekubona nekukala emakhoyili, kwaba yintfo leyentiwa kutsi leligama lelitsi Geiger Counter.
Njengoba bekungumshini wesayensi kusukela ngaleso sikhatsi, iGeiger counter yaphindze yaba ngumshini wesintfu, njengasesimeni se 1950 "Bells of Coronado", lesadlala bososayensi labatsandvwa kakhulu labatiwa ngekutsi ngema cowboy, Roy Rogers na Dale Evans:
Indvodza: "Yini leyo?"
Rogers: "Lena yi Geiger counter, isetjentiswa kutfola indzawo yemaminerali lanemsakato, njenge uranium.
Nawusebentisa letindlebe, ungava umphumela wema-athomu lokhishwa yimisebe yemandla emvelo etintfweni letincane".
Evans: "Khuluma, kufanele kutsi nyalo sewukhona!"
"Hans" Geiger wafa nga-1945, emalanga lambalwa nje ngaphambi kwekugubha iminyaka lengu-63 atelwe.
