Umjovo lomusha wekulapha umdlavuza ufundzisa umtimba wakho kutsi "ubone" emangcoliso
Lomutsi lomusha wekugoma umdlavuza ufundzisa umtimba wakho kutsi ukhone kubona emangcoliso bese uyawabulala
Lomjovo ufundzisa umtimba wakho kutsi ubone emagciwane njengencenye yemutsi
Indlela yakhe yekwenta loku ifaka ekhatsi kukhipha emangcoliso etinhlayiyeni temtimba kumuntfu logulako, bese uyashintja.
Bangakhona kubona emaprotheni lavamile kumdlavuza lomnyenti bese bayakufaka.
Umutsi wekugoma wetilingo ukhombisa imiphumela lemihle etigulini letinetinhlobo letehlukene temdlavuza.
Lomunye wesifazane lowatfola lomjovo, lofundzisa umtimba wakhe kutsi ubone emagciwane, waba nesifo semdlavuza wemaqanda, waphila tinyanga letingu-18.
Lendlela ifaka ekhatsi kukhipha emangcoliso etinhlayiyeni temuntfu, kuwashintja emisebentini yemvelo kute akwati kubona liphoyinti lelibitwa ngekutsi yi-HER2 lelivetwa tifo letinyenti, bese uyawatsatsa uwabeke emuva.
Phrofesa Jay Berzofsky, wase-United States National Cancer Institute eBethesda, eMaryland, utsi: "Loku lokwentekile kukhombisa kutsi sinemutsi lokhombisa litsemba".
I-HER2 "ikhutsata kukhula kwetinhlobo letinyenti temdlavuza", lokufaka ekhatsi umhlabatsi wemabele, wema-ovari, wemaphaphu kanye newemabele, kuchaza Profesa Berzofsky.
Indlela lefanako yekutsatsa emangcoliso emuntfu bese "sifundzisa" kutsi angawatsatsa njani lamangcoliso, iphumelele ekwelapheni luhlobo lunye lwe-leukemia.
