Kit Harington, longumdlali lomkhulu we Game of Thrones, ugceka bulili lobunebungoti
Kit Harington watiwa kakhulu ngekusebentisa inkemba yakhe njengendvodza lenguJon Snow ku-HBO Game of Thrones.
Kodvwa lomdlali, 31, uphikisana netimo te-macho hero, utsi imisebenti lenjalo isenta kutsi bantfwana labasebasha bavame kucabanga kutsi kufanele babe nemandla kute bahlonishwe.
Akhuluma ne The Sunday Times Culture, Kit watsi uyakholwa kutsi 'kunalokutsite lokungakalungi' futsi uyabuta kutsi angatiphatsa njani tinkinga letimbi tebufana esikhatsini se #MeToo.
Kit, losandza kushada nalomunye wakhe longumlingisi ku-"Game of Thrones" Rose Leslie, naye loneminyaka lengu-31, utsi utiva 'acinile' nakukhulunywa ngalendzaba.
'Ngiva nginemandla kakhulu, nyalo - yini lesiphambanisako kuloku lokushiwo ngemuntfu?' washo njalo.
'Yini lesiyifundzisa emadvodza lamadzala mayelana netinkinga lesibukene nato nyalo?'
Kit ukholelwa kutsi ithelevishini ingaba nesandla ekuveleni kwebantfu labamnyama labadvuna ngebantfu labadvuna kakhulu.
Wachubeka watsi: 'Bobani bantfu labatalwa banjalo futsi yini labafundziswa yona?
Yini lesiyifundziswa kuTV, nasetitaladini, leyenta umfana acabange kutsi kufanele abe naloluhlobo lwendvodza?
Ngicabanga kutsi ngulomunye wemibuto lemikhulu nyalo - singakushintja njani?
Ngobe kukhona lokungakalungi ngalabasha.'
Kulengcociswano waphindze wavuma kutsi angeke adlale kulesitfombe lesilandzelako nobe kulesilandzelako se-Game of Thrones ngesikhatsi loluhlelo luphela ehlobo lelitako, watsi 'uphelile ngemasotja kanye nemahhashi.'
Kusukela ngaNovemba Kit utawuba yinkanyeli ekubuyeleni kwaSam Shepard e-True West, indzaba lemayelana nemkhicito wemafilimu kanye nemnakabo, lobekaligebengu.
Lomlingisi muva nje uveze kutsi kuhlangana nemkakhe Rose bekusizatfu lesihle sekuphuma ku-Game of Thrones.
'Ngakhandza umkami kulomdlalo, ngako-ke wanginika umndeni lotangiphatsa, futsi lapha ngicala khona kuphila kwami,' washo njalo.
Rose udlala Ygritte, umlingisi lotsandvwa nguJon Snow, kulesitfombe lesinemphumelelo se-Emmy.
Labashadako bashada ngaJuni 2018 endzaweni lebeyihlala umndeni wakaLeslie eScotland.
I-HIV/AIDS: I-China ibika kukhuphuka lokungu-14% kwetigameko letinsha
I-China imemetele kukhuphuka kwa-14% kwelinani lebantfu labaphila ne-HIV ne-AIDS.
Tisebenti tetemphilo titsi bantfu labangetulu kwa-820 000 labangenwa ngulesifo kulelive.
Bantfu labangu-40 000 labambalwa babikwe ngekugula ngekota yesibili ya-2018.
Linyenti lalabantfu labasandza kutfolakele liguliswa ngekwelicansi, lokukhombisa kutsi sekwenteke lushintjo lolukhulu.
Ngalokwetayelekile, i-HIV isakateka ngekushesha etindzaweni letinyenti taseShayina ngenca yekumpontshelwa ingati lenesifo.
Nanobe kunjalo, linani lebantfu labangenwa yi-HIV ngalendlela lelisetulu lehle lacishe laba ngukungenwa yi-HIV, kusho tiphatsimandla tetemphilo taseShayina enkomfeni leseYunnan.
Kodvwa umnyaka nemnyaka, linani lebantfu labane-HIV ne-AIDS eChina lenyuke lafika ku-100 000.
Kutseleleka nge-HIV ngekwelicansi kuyinkinga lenkhulu emphakatsini we-LGBT waseShayina.
Buntfu bebulili lobufanako buye bavalwa eChina nga-1997, kepha kubandlulula bantfu be-LGBT kuyachubeka.
Ngenca yemagugu lamasha alelive, lucwaningo lukhombisa kutsi emadvodza lasebenta nebantfu bebulili lobufanako lasemkhatsini wa-70 na-90 ekhulwini atawugcine ashade nemfati.
Kuguliswa lokunyenti kubangelwa kungativikeleli kahle ngekwelicansi.
Kusukela nga-2003, hulumende waseShayina wetsembise kutsi utawuniketa wonkhe umuntfu lusito lwekwelapha i-HIV njengencenye yemitamo yekubukana nalesimo.
Maxine Waters uphikisa kutsi basebenti bakhe bacoce ngemininingwane yemalunga e-GOP, basakata 'emanga lanengoti' kanye 'netinhlelo tekuhlela emanga'
Ummeli we-United States Maxine Waters ngeMgcibelo waphika kutsi lomunye webasebenti bakhe utfumele imininingwane yebantfu labatsatfu labangu-US Republican Senators ku-Wikipedia ye-parliamentarians.
I-Los Angeles Democratic Party icaphelisa kutsi loku kucashwa kwetintfo kuhanjiswa bacwaningi kanye netinhlelo te-website letisebenta ngeligama lelisetulu.
Waters watsi: "Bemanga, emanga, nemanga lamanyenti lanelunya", kusho Waters esitatimendeni sakhe kuTwitter.
Kubikwa kutsi lolwati lolukhishiwe lufaka ekhatsi likheli lendlu nelinani letincingo teSincoma saseMelika Lindsey Graham waseNingizimu Carolina, kanye naMike Lee kanye na-Orrin Hatch, bonkhe base Utah.
Lwati lwavela ku-internet ngeLesihlanu, lwendluliselwa bantfu labangatiwa eCapitol Hill ngesikhatsi kunenchubo yekulalelwa kwelicala le-Senate mayelana nekuhlukunyetwa kwebavoti labangafuni kuba seNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh.
Loku kwavela ngemuva kwekutsi boSodolobha labatsatfu babuta Kavanaugh.
Tindzawo letitsite letifana neGateway Pundit neRedState titsi i-IP lekhomba kutsi ngabe lomlayeto uvela kuphi ihlangene nelihhovisi laWater futsi yembule imininingwane yelinye lisebenti laWater, kusho Hill.
Waters wachubeka watsi: "Loku kumangalelwa lokungasekelwa lutfo kungemanga futsi kungemanga laluhlata".
"Emalunga embutfo wami - labatiwa, imininingwane yabo kanye nekuphepha kwabo kusengotini ngenca yetinsolo tekukhohlisa - abenti lutfo loluletsa kutsi kube nalokuvuza.
Loku kumangalelwa kungemanga futsi kungemanga laluhlata".
Lesitatimende saWatersi saphutfuma kutsi sibangele kuphikiswa ku-internet, lokufaka ekhatsi nalobekangumcondzisi we-White House Press Secretary, Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer wabhala: "Loku kuvukela kusho kutfukutsela.
"Loku kukhombisa kutsi akasiyo lilunga leKhomishane.
Nangabe umuntfu abekwa licala langakalenti, akukafaneli atfukutsele.
Akukafaneli baphambuke.
Akukafaneli babutse umbiko ngesizatfu saloko lokwentekile.
Kufanele kutsi batfobekile futsi batfobekile".
Fleischer wavela acatsanisa indlela Waters lativa ngayo ngekugceka kwebaDemocrats ngeJaji Kavanaugh, labamsola ngekutsi abonakale atfukutsele kakhulu ngesikhatsi sekulalelwa kwelicala ngaLesine.
Omar Navarro, umcashi we-Republican lofuna kubamba Waters elukhetfweni lwesikhatsi lesisemkhatsini, naye waveta umbono wakhe ku-Twitter.
"Kukhulu uma kuliciniso", wabhala kuTwitter.
Watsi: "Bantfu lababi labahlala lapha emhlabeni bayasishaya".
"Sitawucinisekisa kutsi labenti baloku bayavetwa", wachubeka, "bese babaphendvulela ngekwemtsetfo ngetento tabo letilimata futsi letiyingoti kuloyo naloyo muntfu losebentela mine".
Johnny English Strikes Again - Rowan Atkinson's less-than-good spy parody
Nyalo kufuna kubaluleka kweBrexit kuleyo naleyo filimu lensha lenemcondvo loliphutsa ngeBrithani sekuyinsika futsi loko kubonakala kusebenta ekuvuseleleni i-franchise yekudlala-emahlaya ye-parody Johnny English - leyacala nga-2003 na Johnny English yaphindze yaphila nga-2011 na Johnny English Reborn.
Kutawusho kutsi kunemsindvo wekutsi sisengotini lenkhulu yini kutsi kube litfuba lelisha lekutfumela tintfo kulelive?
Nobe kunjalo, Johnny English lonemehlo lamakhulu, buso lobucinile nalongakwati kwenta lutfo, sewuphindze wavuselela ilayisensi yakhe yekwenta tintfo letimbi kwesibili - ligama lakhe lisho ngalokukhulu kunaloko kutsi usidalwa lesinemandla sekusebentisa emahlaya lesakhelwe tindzawo letingakhulumi siNgisi.
Bekangumuntfu loyingcweti yetemfihlo, futsi, nanobe bekati kutsi utawenta njalo, bekanelucetu lwebuntfu baClouseau, incenye yebuntfu baMnumzane Bean kanye nelucetu lwebantfu labahamba ngetinyawo lebebafaka sandla kulenkondlo ye-Chariots of Fire emcimbini wekuvula ema-Olympic aseLondon nga-2012.
Ecinisweni, bekasekelwe kulomunye umhambi kanye nendvodza lengummangaliso yemhlaba wonkhe lebeyake yadlalwa ngu-Atkinson kumakhangisi we-TV i-Barclaycard losele akhohliwe, ashiya inhlekelele ngemuva kwakhe.
Kukhona intfo yinye nobe letimbili letijabulisako kuloluhambo lwami lwamuva.
Ngiyakutsandza kubona Johnny English asondzela kulelihlikhophi agcoke ingubo yesikhumba yasendvulo kanye nemoya lohamba ngemandla lohlala etulu esihlokweni sakhe.
Atkinson bekanendzaba yekuhlekisa ngekwemtimba, kepha kuhlekisa kwakhe bekubonakala kungasebenti kahle futsi kungakavami, ikakhulukati ngesikhatsi emafilimu "labalulekile" lafana na-007 kanye neMishini Lengenakwenteka atimisela kufaka kuhlekisa njengentfo.
Umsindvo wakhe bewubonakala shengatsi ubhekiswe kubantfwana kunebantfu labadzala, futsi kimi, tinhlobonhlobo temahloni aJohnny English betingabi nemcondvo lomusha futsi betigxile emahlaya e-Atkinson etitfombeni letitimungulu.
Lokunye lokwaphutfuma eminyakeni leminyenti kutsi iNgilandi isesimeni lesimatima.
Umuntfu lobanjwa tinhlelo te-Internet ungene ku-website ye-UK leyimfihlo, waveta kutsi bobani bonkhe labasebenti base-UK labasemsebentini, kute advumate labo labasebenta - lokubuhlungu kutsi bekulilunga lelincane la-Kevin Eldon.
Lona bekungumsebenti wekugcina walendvuna-nkulu lebeyinenhlitiyo lembi futsi lebeyingafuni muntfu, lebeyicedze kutandvwa kwakhe kutepolitiki: Emma Thompson bekadlala kahle kakhulu ngemlingisi wakhe lofana naTeresa-May kepha bekete lokunyenti lokwakungentiwa kulombhalo.
Umeluleki wakhe lonelwati wamtjela kutsi njengobe tonkhe tinhloli letisebentako setiphelelwe ngemandla, kufanele akhiphe umuntfu emndenini wakhe.
Loku kusho kutsi Johnny English lobekahleti emgwacweni, nyalo usebenta njengenhloko yesikolwa kuletinye takhiwo letiphakeme, kepha usiniketa tifundvo letiyimfihlo tekusebenta ngekutifihla: kunemahlaya lamahle lapha, ngesikhatsi English aniketa tikolwa tebutse njengeSchool of Rock.
