Yini i-Global Citizen Festival futsi ngabe loku kwente lokutsite yini kunciphisa buphuya?
NgaLesihlanu, iNew York itawuba ne-Global Citizen Festival, umcimbi wemculo wemnyaka lonetinkhanyeti letinyenti letinemidlalo lemangalisako, futsi lenemsebenti longasoze walibaleka; wekucedza buphuya emhlabeni.
Nyalo, ngemnyaka wayo wesikhombisa, lomkhosi we Global Citizen Festival utawubona emashumi etinkhulungwane tebantfu bagcwala iGreat Lawn lese Central Park hhayi nje kuphela kute batfokote ngemsebenti wa Janet Jackson, Cardi B, kanye na Shawn Mendes, kepha futsi nekwenyusa kwati ngemgomo walomkhosi wekucedza buphuya lobukhulu nga 2030.
Umkhosi webahlali bemhlaba wonkhe, lowacala nga-2012, kungumlandvo weLuphiko Lwemhlabawonkhe, licembu lebugebengu lamazwe ngemave lelifuna kucedza buphuya ngekukhulisa linani lebantfu labakhutsele kulwa nebuphuya.
Kute utfole emathikithi amahhala alomcimbi (ngaphandle nangabe ufuna kukhokhela emathikithi e-VIP), bantfu labatawubakhona kulomcimbi kufanele bacedze umsebenti lotsite nobe tento njengekutivumela, kutfumela ema-imeyili kubaholi bemhlaba, kubita, nobe letinye tindlela letisebentisekako tekusita kukhulisa lwati ngemgomo wabo wekucedza buphuya.
Kodvwa-ke, ingabe i-Global Citizen yente kahle kangakanani kuleminyaka lengu-12 leyendlulile ekufezeni lemigomo yayo?
Ngabe lomcabango wekupha bantfu imicimbi mahhala uyindlela lekahle yekukhutsata bantfu kutsi bente lokutsite, nobe ngulenye nje indlela yekukhutsata bantfu kutsi bente lokutsite - bantfu bacabanga kutsi benta umehluko ngekusayina sicelo nobe ngekutfumela i-tweet?
Kusukela nga-2011, i-Global Citizen itsi ibhale ngetulu kwetigidzi letingu-19 "tento" tebantfu labamsekelako, lokukhutsata kutsi abeke letinye tinhloso.
Kutsiwa loku kusite kugcugcutela baholi bemhlaba kutsi bamemetele kutibophetela netinhlelo letingaba ngemarandi langetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-37 letitawutsintsa bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-2.25 nga-2030.
Ekucaleni kwa-2018, lelicembu selibutse tibophetelo letingu-390 kanye netimemetelo letivelako temisebenti yalo, lokungenani tigidzigidzi leti-10 temali letakhishwa nobe letakhishwa.
Lelicembu licabanga kutsi imali lephephile seyivele yente umtselela kubantfu labacishe babe tigidzi letingu-649 emhlabeni wonkhe.
Letinye tetetsembiso letibalulekile nguleti: I-Power of Nutrition, budlelwane lobusekelwe e-UK lobubunjwa batsengisi kanye netisebenti letibopheleke ekusiteni bantfwana kutsi "bakhule kute bafinyelele emakhono abo", yetsembisa kuniketa i-Rwanda tigidzi letingu-35 tetigidzi temarandi kute isite ekucedzeni kungondleki kahle kulelive ngemuva kwekutfola ema-tweets langetulu kwa-4 700 lavela ku-Global Citizen.
"Ngekusekelwa nguhulumende waseNgilandi, banikeli, bohulumende bemave, kanye nebantfu labaphila njengani, singenta lokungalungi lokwenteka kubantfu labaphuyile kudla kube yintfo leyenteka emlandvweni", kusho ummeli we The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, atjela sicumbi sebantfu ngesikhatsi sekuchubeka kwemkhosi wakhe eLondon nga-Apreli 2018.
Lelicembu liphindze litsi ngemuva kwetento letingetulu kwa-5 000 tekwenta ncono kudla kwemake nebantfwana e-UK, hulumende umemetele kutfola imali yelihhovisi lemklamo, i-Power of Nutrition, letawufinyelela bantfu labasikati nebantfwana labatigidzi letisihlanu ngekudla.
