I-US ingasebentisa umbutfo wemikhumbi njengendlela yekugadza kutsengiswa kwagezi waseRussia - Umcondzisi weTasekhaya
"Nangabe kudzingeka" iWashington ingacela lusito lweMkhumbi weTekuvikela kuvimbela emandla aseRussia kutsi angafiki etimakethe, kufaka ekhatsi eMiddle East, kusho iNdvuna yeTasekhaya yaseMelika, Ryan Zinke, njengobe acashunwe yiWashington Examiner.
Zinke usola kakhulu kutsi kungenelela kweRussia eSyria - ikakhulukati, lapho khona isebenta ngekumenywa nguhulumende lowemukelekile - kusento sekuhlola timakethe letinsha temandla.
"Ngicabanga kutsi sizatfu sabo sekuba seMiddle East kutsi bafuna kuba batsengisi betintfo temandla agezi, njengobe benta e-Eastern Europe, eningizimu ye-Europe", kubika yena.
Ngekusho kwalesikhulu, kunetindlela tekuvimbela loku.
"I-United States inalo likhono, neLwandle Lwetfu, lekucinisekisa kutsi indlela yemanti ivulekile, futsi, uma kudzingeka, kwenta sivinjelwe, kucinisekisa kutsi emandla abo angeke angene etimakethe", kusho yena.
Zinke abekhuluma emhlanganweni lobewubanjwe yi-Consumer Energy Alliance, licembu lelingasebenti ngemali lelitibita ngekutsi "ligama lebatsengi bemandla" eMelika.
Wakhombisa kutsi indlela iWashington leyenta ngayo kulesivumelwano neRussia ne Iran, wabona kutsi ngekusebenta kahle, iyafana.
"Lokukhetfwa kutemnotfo e-Iran naseRussia, cishe, kusebentisa kanye nekusebentisa letinye tifutfo", washo, akhuluma ngeRussia njengalomunye "lowati kahle lomkhakha" ngemnotfo lotsembele ku-fossil fuel.
Lesitatimende sifika ngesikhatsi emalunga ahulumende waTrump enta umsebenti wekukhulisa kutsengiswa kwegesi yemvelo eYurophu, esikhundleni seRussia, intfo lephephile kubatsengi baseYurophu.
Kute kufinyelelwe loku, tikhulu tehulumende baka Trump, kufaka ekhatsi Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump, betama kwenta kutsi iJalimane iyekele lomklamo we Nord Stream 2 "longakafaneli", lowenta iBerlin ibe "sitsa" se Moscow.
IMoscow igcizelele kanyenti kutsi lomklamo we-Nord Stream 2 lotigidzigidzi temadola letingu-11 wemanti, lohloswe kutsi uphindze ube nemandla ekufaka ema-cubic metres latigidzi leti-110 emanti, ngumklamo wetemnotfo kuphela.
I-Kremlin iphikisana ngekutsi kuphikisa kwaWashington lokumatima kwaloluhlelo bekugcizelelwa tizatfu tetemnotfo kuphela futsi bekungumfanekiso wekuncintisana lokungakalungi.
"Ngicabanga kutsi sinembono lofanako wekutsi emandla agezi akukafaneli asetjentiswe njengentfo yekucindzetela nekutsi emakhasimende kumele akhone kutimela kutsi ngubani lotawubasekela", kusho iNdvuna yeTemandla yaseRussia Alexander Novak ngemuva kwemhlangano neNdvuna yeTemandla yaseMelika Rick Perry eMoscow ngaSeptember.
Lesimo seMelika sibangele kuphikisana nemaJalimane, laphindze avumelana ngalomklamo.
Inhlangano yetimboni yaseJalimane, iFederation of German Industries (BDI), icele iMelika kutsi ingangeneli kutinhlelo te-European Union tetemandla kanye netivumelwano temave lamabili emkhatsini we Berlin ne Moscow.
"Ngitawubhekana netinkinga letinkhulu nangabe emave esitsatfu angenelela ekunikeni emandla etfu", kusho Dieter Kempf, inhloko yeFederation of German Industries (BDI) ngemuva kwemhlangano lomusha emkhatsini waMengameli waseJalimane Angela Merkel neMengameli waseRussia Vladimir Putin.
