Ngemuva kweliviki liphephandaba lelisemtsetfweni laseChina liphephe likhangiso lesemakhasi lamane kulelinye liphephandaba laseMelika lelisho kutsi kunenzuzo yekuhwebelana kwe-US ne-China, ummeli waseMelika eChina usola iBeijing ngekusebentisa emaphephandzaba aseMelika kute asakaze inkhulumo-mphikiswano.
Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump ngaLwesitsatfu weta nesitfunywa sakhe lesikhokhelwa iChina Daily kuDes Moines Register - phephandaba lelibaluleke kakhulu e-Iowa - ngemuva kwekusola iChina ngekufuna kungenela lukhetfo lwe-US lwekungenela umkhandlu ngaNovemba 6, lokuyintfo lephikiswa yiChina.
Kusola kwaTrump kutsi iBeijing yetama kungenela lukhetfo lwaseMelika, lokusho loko lokwashiwo sikhulu saseMelika kuReuters, kusesigabeni lesisha semkhankhaso lowakhiwe yiWashington wekucindzetela iChina.
Nanobe kuvamile kutsi bohulumende bangaphandle bafake tikhangiso kute bakhutsate kutsengiselana, nyalo iBeijing neWashington bagcwele timphi tekutsengiselana, lokwenta kutsi banyuse emazinga etintsela kulomunye nalomunye.
Letintsela tekuphindzisela tase China ekucaleni kwemphi yekuhwebelana tihloselwe kuhlasela batsengisi betimphahla emaveni lafana ne Iowa lasekela licembu le Trump Republican Party, kusho tati te US ne China.
Terry Branstad, lithunywa laseMelika eChina kanye nembusi wangaphambilini wesikhatsi lesidze wase-Iowa, longumtsengisi lomkhulu wetintfo tekulima eChina, watsi iBeijing ihlukubeta tisebenti, balimi, kanye nebosomabhizinisi baseMelika.
