Bacwaningi bayacwayisa, liCembu lemaRephabliki litawukhipha bantfu labasikati ekuvoteni ngaphambi kwelukhetfo lwesikhatsi lesisemkhatsini ngenca yenhlekelele yaKavanaugh
Ngenca yetintfo letinyenti letibalulekile te-Republican letimelela umengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh ekubukeni emacala ekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi, bacwaningi bayacwayisa kutsi batawubona kuphendvuka, ikakhulukati kusuka kubomake, elukhetfweni lolutako lwesikhatsi lesisemkhatsini.
Umdlandla ngalendzaba uphezulu kakhulu, futsi linyenti lemaRephabliki selivele likhombisile kutsi lifuna kuchubeka nekuvota.
Loku akukafaneli kuvinjelwe", Grant Reeher, longulomunye wabofundzisi betembusave eMexwell School, eSyracuse University, watjela iThe Hill ngesihloko lesashicilelwa ngaMgcibelo.
Reeher utsi uyabuta kutsi ngabe umfutfo weSincumo seMengameli (we-R-Arizona) Jeff Flake wekugcina wekwenta luphenyo lwe-FBI utawuba ngulolwenele yini kute kucedvwe intfukutselo yalabo labavoti.
"Bantfu labasikati angeke bakukhohlwe lokwenteka itolo - angeke bakukhohlwe kusasa, futsi angeke bakukhohlwe ngaNovemba", kusho Karine Jean-Pierre, longumeluleki lomkhulu kanye nesikhulumi savelonkhe selicembu lelitimbandzakanya ne-progressive MoveOn, ngeLesihlanu, ngekusho kweliphephandzaba laseWashington, D.C.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, babhikishi bamemeta batsi "November is near!" ngesikhatsi babhikisha egumbini leSenate ngesikhatsi emaRephabliki alawula Likomidi Lebugebengu kutsi achubeke nekubeka Kavanaugh esikhundleni nanobe bekunembono waDkt Christine Blasey Ford, kubika iMic.
"Umdlandla kanye nekugcugcutela intsandvo yelinyenti kutawususwa kuloluhlu", kusho umhlatiyi wepolitiki longenawo emacembu Stu Rothenberg, watjela i-website yetindzaba.
"Bantfu batsi seyiphakeme kakhulu, futsi kuliciniso.
Kodvwa kungenteka kutsi tibe ngetulu kakhulu, ikakhulukati emkhatsini webantfu labamnyama labavota etindzaweni letisemaphandleni kanye nebantfu labasebasha, labaneminyaka lengu-18 kuya ku-29, labangafuni kuba nemengameli, futsi labavame kungavoti".
Ngisho nangaphambi kwekufakaza kwaFord embikwebantfu lokuchaza kabanti ngekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi kwakhe ngulomuntfu lobekafuna kuba ngumengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme, bacwaningi bebalumkise kutsi kutawuba nekulwa lokulandzelako uma ngabe emaRephabliki achubeka nekumkhutsata kutsi achubeke nekucinisekisa.
"Loku kwaba yintfo lematima kakhulu ku-GOP", Michael Steele, lobekangusihlalo welikomidi le-Republican National Committee, watjela i-NBC News ekucaleni kweliviki leliphelile.
"Loku akusiko nje kukhetsa likomidi nobe kukhetsa lokugcina nobe kutsi ngabe Kavanaugh utawugcinwa yini esihlalweni sekugcina, kuphindze kube yindlela emaRephabliki latawubukana ngayo naloludzaba nekutsi atawuphatsa njani", kusho Guy Cecil, longumcondzisi we Priorities USA, licembu lelisita kukhetsa emaDemocrats, akhomba siteshi setindzaba.
Nobe kunjalo, bantfu baseMelika babonakala behlukene ekhatsi mayelana nekutsi ngubani labamtsembako ngemuva kwekubekwa licala kwaFord naKavanaugh, ngekukhetsa lokuncane lokutsandza lona wekugcina.
Luhlolo lolusha lolwentiwe yi-YouGov lukhombisa kutsi 41% webantfu labaphendvule bakholwa nobe bangakholelwa kufakazi waFord, kantsi 35% batsi bayakholelwa nobe bangakholelwa kuKavanaugh.
Ngetulu kwaloko, bantfu labangu-38% batsi bacabanga kutsi Kavanaugh kungenteka nobe ucala emanga ngesikhatsi afakaza, kantsi bantfu labangu-30% batsi naye Ford.
Ngemuva kwekucelwa nguFlake, i-FBI nyalo iyaphenya ngetinsolo letentiwa nguFord kanye nalomunye lobekacala, Deborah Ramirez, iThe Guardian ibika.
Ford wafakaza ngaphansi kwesifungo ngaphambi kwelikomidi le-Senate Judiciary kutsi Kavanaugh lobekanatse kakhulu wamhlasela ngesikhatsi aneminyaka lengu-17.
Ramirez watsi lomuntfu lobekafuna kuba nguMengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme wamkhombisa titfo takhe tangasese ngesikhatsi baya emcimbini ngesikhatsi bafundza e-Yale ngabo-1980.
Umsunguli we-World Wide Web Ufuna Kucala I-Internet Lensha Kute Alwe Na-Google Na-Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, umsunguli weWebhu, wacalisa inhlangano lebeyifuna kuchudzelana neFacebook, Amazon neGoogle.
Umklamo lomusha walesichwephesha lesatiwa kakhulu, i-Inrupt, yinkampani leyakhiwe nge-platform yemtfombo levulekile yaBerners-Lee, i-Solid.
I-Solid ivumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse kutsi idatha yabo igcinwa kuphi nekutsi ngubani lofanele afinyelele kuyo.
Kulengcoco leyayibanjwe ne Fast Company, Berners-Lee watsi injongo ye-Inrupt "kukubusa umhlaba".
"Kufanele sicale nyalo", kwasho yena.
"Lona ngumzuzu lomcoka".
Lolusito lusebentisa buchwepheshe be Solid lobuvumela bantfu kutsi bakhe "umshini wabo wekugcina imininingwane ku-inthanethi" nobe i-POD.
Leso sitolo singaba neluhla lwekukhuluma, luhlu lwemisebenti, likhalenda, umtapo wetingoma, kanye naletinye tintfo takho kanye netintfo tekusebenta.
NjengaseGoogle Drive, iMicrosoft Outlook, iSlack, neSpotify, konkhe kufinyeleleka kusiphequluli sinye futsi konkhe ngesikhatsi sinye.
Lokwehlukile ngaloluhlobo lwekugcina imininingwane yangasese ku-inthanethi kutsi kukhetsa kutsi ngubani longasebentisa loluhlobo lwemininingwane.
Emkhakheni wetekukhicita, loku kubitwa ngekutsi "kucinisa umuntfu ngemininingwane".
Umbono wekusungula i-Inrupt, ngekusho kwa-CEO wayo John Bruce, kutsi inkampani inikete imitfombolusito lefanele, tinchubo kanye nemakhono ekusita kwenta i-Solid itfolakale kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Nyalo lenkapani ibunjwe nguBerners-Lee, Bruce, luhlaka lwekuphepha lolutsengwe yi-IBM, basebenti labatsite labatsite labatsenge umsebenti, kanye nemphakatsi wetisebenti letivolontiya letibhalako.
Kusukela kuleliviki, batfutfukisi betekuhweba emhlabeni wonkhe bangakhona kwakha tinhlelo tabo tekuhweba letingalawulwa basebentisa emathulusi latfolakala kuwebhusayithi ye-Inrupt.
Berners-Lee watsi yena nelicembu lakhe abazange bakhulume ne "Facebook neGoogle mayelana nekutsi batawungenisa nobe cha ingucuko lenkhulu lapho khona yonkhe imodeli yebhizinisi yabo itawuguculwa ngalokuphelele ngalobunye busuku.
"Asikabaceli kutsi basivumele".
Encwadzini yakhe letsi Medium leyatfolakala ngeMgcibelo, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi "umsebenti we-Inrupt kuniketa emandla kanye nemvelo yetentengiso kute kusitwe kuvikela bucotfo nekhwalithi yewebhu lensha leyakhiwe nge Solid".
Nga-1994, Berners-Lee washintja i-Internet ngesikhatsi asungula i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile, Berners-Lee ube livi lelibalulekile ekuvikeleni kungakhetsi kwetinkundla.
Ngisho nangesikhatsi asungula i-Inrupt, Berners-Lee utawuhlala angumsunguli kanye neMcondzisi we-World Wide Web Consortium, iWeb Foundation, kanye ne-Open Data Institute.
"Nginelitsemba lelikhulu nge-web era lelandzelako", kwengeta Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: kukhumbula umfundisi we WW1 Victoria Cross
Umfundisi weLisontfo waseNgilandi lowancoba iVictoria Cross ngesikhatsi semphi yelive yekucala njengelisotja, ukhunjulwa eveni lakubo eminyakeni lelikhulu leyendlulile.
Lithenwa-Kolonel The Reverend, Bernard Vann watfola lomklomelo mhlaka 29 Inyoni 1918 ngekuhlasela eBellenglise nase Lehaucourt.
Nobe kunjalo, ngemuva kwemalanga lamane wabulawa ngemasotja labetfwele tiboshwa letincane futsi akazange ati kutsi sewuwine umklomelo lomkhulu webutfo bemaNgisi.
Litje lesikhumbuto lavulwa batukulu bakhe lababili emkhosini waseRushden, eNorthamptonshire, ngeMgcibelo.
Lomunye wemtukulu wakhe, Michael Vann, watsi leli litje "lisibonakaliso sekuhlakanipha" lesitawukhombisa iminyaka lelikhulu yekuphumelela kwayisemkhulu wakhe.
Ngekusho kwe-London Gazette, ngaSeptember 29, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann wahola libuthwana lakhe lawela i-Canal de Saint-Quentin "libhodla ngaphansi kwetibhamu letinkhulu temasotja".
Ngemuva kwaloko, wagijimela emgceni wemphi futsi "ngesibindzi lesikhulu" wahola umzabalazo ngaphambi kwekutsi asebentise tikhali takhe yedvwa futsi akhubaze emabutfo lamatsatfu.
Lithenwa-Kholikheli Vann wabulawa ngemasotja aseJalimane nga-October 4, 1918 - lokwasekusele inyanga kutsi kuphele imphi.
Michael Vann, loneminyaka lengu-72, watsi loko lokwentiwa ngugogo wakhe "kwakuyintfo lebengati kutsi angeke ngiphile ngayo kodvwa bekusento sekutfobeka lokukhulu".
Yena nemnakabo Dokotela James Vann nabo bafaka emacembe ngemuva kwemkhosi, lowaholwa yiBrentwood Imperial Youth Band.
Michael Vann watsi "ujabulile kakhulu ngekubamba lichaza kulomkhosi" futsi wachubeka watsi "kuba nesibindzi kwemachawe eliciniso kukhonjiswa ngekwesekelwa bantfu labanyenti".
Bantfu labatsandza iMMA bahlala ebusuku babukele i-Bellator 206 kodvwa esikhundleni saloko batfola i-Peppa Pig
Asewucabange nje, ubephapheme busuku bonkhe ubuka i-Bellator 206 lenetfwele bantfu labanyenti, kodvwa sewulahliwe kubona umbukiso loyinhloko.
Umtsetfo waseSan Jose ucuketse timphi letingu 13, kufaka ekhatsi letisitfupha letisemakhadi ekucala futsi usakata bukhoma busuku bonkhe eNgilandi ku Channel 5.
Nga-6 ekuseni, ngesikhatsi Gegard Mousasi naRory MacDonald balungiselela kubambana, babukeli baseNgilandi bamangala ngesikhatsi umbiko wakhe ugucuka waba nguPeppa Pig.
Labanye bantfu bativa bangakabongwa ngemuva kwekuba sebahlale sikhatsi lesidze ngelilanga lemphi.
Lomunye umlandeli kuTwitter wachaza kugucula kwakhe ku-cartoon yebantfwana ngekutsi "ngumdlalo lohluphako".
"Ngumtsetfo wahulumende kutsi nga-6 ekuseni lokucuketfwe akukalungi kutsi kusakatwe, ngako-ke sekufanele kutsi kusakatwe luhlelo lwebantfwana", kwasho Dave Schwartz, longumphatsi lomkhulu we Bellator wekukhangisa nekukhulumisana, nakabutwa ngaloluhlelo.
"Peppa ingulube, yebo".
Umengameli we-Bellator Scott Coker utsi batawulungisa luhlelo lwabo lwekuhlela kute bahloniphe bantfu base-UK esikhatsini lesitako.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma sicabanga ngekuphindza futsi, ngicabanga kutsi singakhona kukwenta loko", kusho Coker.
"Kodvwa nyalo ngelisontfo ekuseni ngensimbi yesitfupha, futsi angeke sikhone kulungisa lomonakalo kute kube liSontfo, sikhatsi setfu, ngeMsombuluko sikhatsi sabo.
Kodvwa siyati kutsi sisuke siyatimisela.
Ngetsembeni, ngesikhatsi sekuntjintja, bekunetincwadzi letinyenti lebetibhalwe phasi futsi tonkhe betingafundzisi.
Sisazama kulungisa, sicabanga kutsi yintfo nje yekuhluleka.
Cha, loko kuyinkinga yahulumende.
Ngetsembe, esikhatsini lesitako angeke kuphindze kwenteke.
Sitawuncishiswa sibe ngimichudzelwano lesihlanu kuphela kunemitsatfu - njengobe besivame kwenta - futsi sitawuzama kugwema kubukela kakhulu kubalandeli, futsi siphumelele.
Loku akusiko lokuhle".
Tom Daley utiva 'ahloniphekile' ngetindzaba tebulili
Tom Daley, longumuntfu lowatfutsela ema-Olympic, utsi wakhula angatihloniphi ngenca yetinkinga takhe tekuya ecasini - kodvwa loko kwamenta watimisela kutsi aphumelele.
Lomuntfu loneminyaka lengu-24 budzala utsi akazange akubone loko waze wangena esikolweni lesisetulu, kutsi "akusibo bonkhe bantfu labafana nami".
Akhuluma kwekucala kuRadio 4 Desert Island Discs leyetfulwa nguLauren Laverne, watsi, ukhuluma ngelilungelo lebantfu labashadile kutsi banike labanye "litsemba".
Waphindze watsi kuba ngumtali kumenta angakhatsateki kakhulu ngekuncoba ema-Olympic.
Umsakazi wetfu losasenesikhatsi lesidze, Kirsty Young, utsatsa tinyanga letimbalwa tekungabikho emsebentini ngenca yekugula.
Njengobe bekabonakala angakafaneli kulesimiso sekucala saLaverne, Daley watsi utiva "angakabaluleki" kunabo bonkhe bantfu labakhula naye ngobe "akwemukeleki emphakatsini kutsandza bantfu bebulili lobutsite".
Utsi: "Nanyalo, lokutiva ngingakalungi, ngicabanga kutsi ngehlukile, kungenta ngibe nemandla ekuphumelela".
Bekafuna kukhombisa kutsi "ungulomunye umuntfu", watsi, kute angadvumati bonkhe bantfu nabatfola kutsi unenkinga yebulili.
Lomdlali lowemukele emabhonasi lamabili ema-Olympic sewungumuntfu lowatiwako lowenta umkhankaso we-LGBT futsi usebentise indlela yakhe yekudlala kuma-Commonwealth Games latawubanjwa e-Australia kulomnyaka kute akhutsate emave lamanyenti kutsi angabandlululi bantfu labatsandzanako.
Watsi ukhuluma ngobe utiva anenhlanhla yekuphila imphilo levulekile futsi lengenabo imiphumela futsi ufuna kuniketa labanye "litsemba".
Lomdlali wemhlaba lophindzaphindziwe katsatfu utsi kutsandzana nalomuntfu - umlingisi waseMelika Dustin Lance Black, lamhlangabeta nga-2013 - "kwangimangaza".
Daley washada nemuntfu lowatfola umklomelo we-Oscar lomdzala kunaye ngeminyaka lengu-20 kulomnyaka lowengcile, futsi watsi budzala bakhe abusiyo inkinga.
"Nawuhlangabetana netinkinga letinyenti usemncane kakhulu" - waya kuma-Olympics akhe ekucala aneminyaka lengu-14 budzala futsi babe wakhe washona ngenca yemdlavuza ngemuva kweminyaka lemitsatfu - utsi kumatima kakhulu kutfola umuntfu wemnyaka wakhe lohlangabetana netinkinga letifanako.
Labashadene baba batali ngaJuni, nemfana lobitwa ngekutsi nguRobert Ray Black-Daley, futsi Daley utsi "lombono wakhe wonkhe" sewushintjile.
"Nangabe ungibuta kulomnyaka lophelile, bekutsiwa 'ngifanele ngiwine indondo yeligolide,'" washo njalo.
"Uyati, kunalokunyenti lokudzingeka kwentiwe kunekumane nje uwine umudvali weligolide ema-Olympic.
Indzebe yami yeligolide yema-Olimpiki nguRobbie".
Indvodzana yakhe inalo ligama lelingilo leyise Robert, lowafa nga-2011 aneminyaka lengu-40 budzala ngemuva kwekubonwa kutsi unesifo semdlavuza engcondvweni.
Daley watsi uyise akakwemukeli kutsi utawufa, futsi intfo yekugcina layibuta kutsi batitfolile yini emathikithi ema-Olimpiki aseLondon yanga-2012 - ngobe abefuna kuhlala emgceni wangembili.
"Angeke ngitsi kuye 'Ungeke uhlale emgceni wangembili babe,'" washo njalo.
"Ngambamba ngesikhatsi aphefumula futsi angizange ngimyekele aze afe, ekugcineni ngavuma kutsi angeke ancobe", washo.
Ngemnyaka lolandzelako Daley wahlanganyela kuma-Olympic ngemnyaka wa-2012 futsi watfola libhonshi.
"Lokunye lengikwatiko kutsi nguloko lebengikufisa imphilo yami yonkhe - kuhamba embikwesicheme sebantfu eMidlalweni Yema-Olympic, kute lokujabulisa kakhulu kunaloko", washo njalo.
Waphindze waphefumulela kukhetsa ingoma yakhe yekucala - Proud by Heather Small - leyavele yamenta wahlangana naye ngesikhatsi alungiselela ema-Olympic futsi isamenta abe nemahloni.
I-Desert Island Discs ngumsakazo we-BBC Radio 4 losakazwa njalo ngeLisontfo nga-11:15 BST.
Mickelson utsatsa indzima yakhe ngesikhatsi ahlanganiswa kuRyder Cup ngeMgcibelo
Umgadli weligalofu waseMelika Phil Mickelson utawubeka umlandvo ngeLisontfo ngesikhatsi adlala umdlalo wakhe we Ryder Cup wesi-47, kepha utawudzinga kushintja tindzima takhe kute agweme umphumelelo longemuhle.
Mickelson, lowadlala kulomdlalo weminyaka lemibili kwentela kubhala umlandvo wekutsi utawudlala sikhatsi lesingu-12, wabekwa ngu-captain Jim Furyk emdlalweni wemabhola lamane kanye nelicembu lelinebantfu labane ngeMgcibelo.
Esikhundleni sekutsi abe semkhatsini wekwenta tintfo, njengobe abevame kwenta eMelika, lomncobi wemidlalo lemikhulu emahlandla lasihlanu wehlukanisa sikhatsi sakhe emkhatsini wekuba ngumkhombandlela wekubonga nekudlala kwakhe kuleso sigaba, etsemba kutsi utawulungisa loko lokwamehlela.
Nanobe bekangasuye umuntfu locondzile, kodvwa ngesikhatsi asemkhatsini webantfu labakhulu, lomuntfu loneminyaka lengu-48 budzala bekangakafaneli kutsi ahambe emabaleni labukhali kakhulu eLe Golf National, lebeyivame kuniketa sigwebo lesidze futsi lesimatima ngemtsamo ngamunye longakalungi.
Futsi ensimini yakhe, bekungesiko kwesaba lokwenele kutsi Mickelson, emdlalweni wesitsatfu ngeLisontfo, abhekane nemchawe we-English Open lociniseke kakhulu Francesco Molinari, lowasebenta nemuntfu lomusha Tommy Fleetwood kute ancobe yonkhe imidlalo yabo lemine kuleliviki.
Nangabe lomgadli waseMelika, locala imidlalo lengu-12 yedvwa aphansi ngemaphuzu lamane, ucala ngekucala lokushisako, umdlalo waMickelson utawuba ngulobaluleke kakhulu.
Furyk ukhombisa kukholwa kulomuntfu, hhayi ngobe angasho lokunyenti.
"Wati kahle kutsi yini lokufanele ayente lamuhla, wangishaya emhlane wangimanga, watsi utawube akulungele kulomdlalo wakusasa", kusho Furyk.
"Uyati kutsi angati kutsi yini lafuna kuyenta.
Ungumdlali lowatiwako futsi unikete kakhulu kulelicembu esikhatsini lesengcile, nakuleliviki.
Mhlawumbe angikwati kumcabanga adlala imidlalo lemibili.
Bengifisa kutsi kube khona labanye, kodvwa nguloko lebesikubona kuyindlela yekudlala futsi nguloko lebesicinga kutsi kufanele sikwente.
Ufuna kujabulela letinye tintfo, njengalabanye bantfu".
Mickelson utawudlula umlandvo waNick Faldo wekudlala imidlalo leminyenti kakhulu ye-Ryder Cup, ngeLisontfo.
Loku kungaphindze kubonise kuphela kwemsebenti wakhe we-Ryder Cup longeke uphindze uhlangane nemlandvo wakhe.
Mickelson wawina emahlandla la-18 ancoba emahlandla la-20, futsi wawina emahlandla lasikhombisa, nanobe Furyk atsi kuba khona kwakhe kwaletsa tintfo letincane kakhulu kulelicembu.
"Uyahlekisa, unelwati, uyahlekisa, utsandza kuhlekisa ngebantfu, futsi ungumuntfu lohloniphekile endlini yekusebenta", kuchaza yena.
"Ngicabanga kutsi labadlali labasebancane bayajabula naye, nakuleliviki, lokuyintfo lenhle kakhulu kutsi uyibuke.
Wenta lokungetulu nje kwekudlala".
Thomas Bjorn, umphatsi waseYurophu bekati kutsi emandla lamakhulu angasheshe aphele.
Thomas Bjorn, longumphatsi we-Europe, wafundza ngekubona kutsi umuntfu lohola kakhulu ekuhambeni kwakhe kwekugcina emdlalweni we-Ryder Cup kungaba luhambo lolungasijabulisi.
Dane wenta kucala kwakhe emdlalweni wanga-1997 eValderrama, na Seve Ballesteros, indvuna yelive, abeneligunya leliphelele leliphelele kumaMelika, kepha wavele wafika entsanjeni ngemphumelelo yabo ngemaphuzu lamancane, ngekuncoba 141⁄2-131⁄2.
"Uchubeka utikhumbuta kutsi sitfole umncono lomkhulu eValderrama; sitfole umncono lomkhulu eBrookline, lapho silahlekelwe khona, naseValderrama, lapho siwine khona, kepha nje", kusho Bjorn, atsatsa titfombe, ngemuva kwekubuka iClass of 2018, incobe nga-5-3 ngaLesihlanu nangakusasa ngekuhola nga-10-6 eLe Golf National.
Ngako-ke, umlandvo utawungikhombisa kanye nabo bonkhe labakulelicembu kutsi loku akukapheli.
Kusasa nitawucala umdlalo longenamsebenti.
Phuma uyewutsandza kwenta lokulungile.
Akukapheli uze utfole emaphuzu ebhodini.
Sinemgomo, futsi lomgomo kuncoba lesigcawu, futsi nguloko lokugcile.
Sengikhulume sikhatsi lesidze kutsi ngigcile kubadlali labangu-12 labaseluhlangotsini lwetfu, kodvwa futsi siyakwati kahle lokwentekile kulolunye luhlangotsi - badlali labakhulu kakhulu emhlabeni".
Bjorn, lojabulako nakabona badlali badlala emgwacweni lomkhulu, uchubeka atsi: "Angeke ngikhone kudlala ngedwa.
Kusasa kutawuba yinkhanyeti leyehlukile.
Kusasa, badlali labatsite batawuchubeka, futsi loku kutawuba nguletinye tintfo letitawentiwa.
Kujabulisa kakhulu kuba semgwacweni nebalingani bakho nangabe tintfo tihamba kahle, kodvwa nawudlala wedvwa, likhono lakho leliphelele njengemdlali weligoli litawuhlolwa.
Lona ngumlayeto lokufanele uwendlulisele kubo bonkhe badlali, kutsi nikhiphe konkhe lokusemandleni enu kulomdlalo wakusasa.
Nyalo, ushiya umlingani wakho futsi kufanele ahambe kute akhiphe lokuncono kakhulu kuye".
Ngalokwehlukile kuBjorn, umphikisi wakhe Jim Furyk utawucela badlali bakhe kutsi badlale kancono ngekwehlukana kunaloko labakwentako njengabaphatsi, ngaphandle kwaJordan Spieth naJustin Thomas, labazuze emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulamane.
Furyk yena bekasesigodzini lesibili emalangeni ekugcina alomdlalo lomkhulu, abeyincenye yelicembu lelaliphumelele eBrookline ngaphambi kwekutsi liphele ngekulahlekelwa ngesikhatsi emave aseYurophu enta "Umlingo waseMedina".
"Ngikhumbula onkhe lamavi", washo aphendvula umbuto wekutsi Ben Crenshaw, indvuna nga-1999, wababeka njani labadlali bakhe ndzawonye kute kube lilanga lekugcina.
"Sinemidlalo le-12 lebalulekile kusasa, kodvwa kufanele sicale masinyane njengobe nibona eBrookline, njengobe nibona eMedina.
Nangabe umfutfo uhamba ngendlela yinye, kutawuba nekucindzeteleka lokukhulu emdlalweni losemkhatsini.
Siphindze sihlele luhlu lwetihambi futsi sibeke bantfu ngetindlela letehlukene lesitiva, niyabona, setama kwenta umlingo kusasa".
Thomas unikwe umsebenti wekutsi afune kuhola umzabalazo lobhekene na Rory McIlroy emdlalweni loyinhloko, na Paul Casey, Justin Rose, Jon Rahm, Tommy Fleetwood, na Ian Poulter, labanye badlali base Europe labasemkhatsini webadlali labakhulu.
"Ngicedze lelicembu lebantfu ngalendlela ngoba ngicabanga kutsi ngingavala yonkhe imigwaco", kusho Bjorn mayelana nekukhetsa kwakhe lokukuphela kwakhe.
Imikhumbi lemikhulu yemphi yemaJalimane yahlehliswa
Umkhumbi lomusha we-German Navy wekulondvolota bekufanele ucale kusebenta nga-2014 kute ulandzele umkhumbi wemphi losemkhatsini weMphi yeBusika, kepha angeke ube khona kuze kube ngumnyaka lotako ngenca yetinkinga tetinhlelo kanye netindleko letinkhulu, kubika imisakato yendzawo.
Umsebenti we "Rheinland-Pfalz", umkhumbi lomkhulu wemikhumbi yekugadza yelicembu lelisha lase Baden-Wuerttemberg, nyalo sewumiswe kwaze kwaba yincenye yekucala yemnyaka wa 2019, kusho iphephandzaba iDie Zeit icaphune sikhulumi sembutfo.
Lomkhumbi bekufanele ujoyine libutho lemphi ngemnyaka wa 2014, kepha tinkinga letisemuva kwekutfunyelwa kwato tiphazamise inhlanhla yaloluhlelo.
Letinkhunzi letine telicembu laseBaden-Wuerttemberg letatfunyelwa emkhosini wemikhumbi ngemnyaka wa 2007 titotsatsa sikhundla semkhumbi welicembu lase Bremen.
Lomkhumbi utawuba nemasotja lanemandla, ema-anti-aircraft kanye nemishini yekulwa nemikhumbi, kanye netintfo letitsite letitfolakala ngekhatsi, njengekucedza i-radar, i-infrared kanye ne-acoustic lock.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile kufaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze sekunakekela - kufanele kube melula kusebentisa umkhumbi lomusha wekulindza iminyaka lemibili usuke endzaweni yakubo.
Nobe kunjalo, kubambezeleka lokukhulu kusho kutsi lemikhumbi lemikhulu - lokutsiwa yenta kutsi emaJalimane akhone kukhombisa emandla awo emaveni angaphandle - itawuphelelwa sikhatsi sayo, kusho i-Die Zeit.
Umkhumbi we-F125 loyinhlanhla lencane waba yindzaba lenkhulu emnyakeni lowengcile, ngesikhatsi libutfo lemikhumbi laseJalimane liwenqaba ngalokusemtsetfweni lomkhumbi futsi liwubuyisela emashayini emikhumbi aseBlohm & Voss eHamburg.
Loku kwekucala kutsi umkhumbi ubuyiselwe kubakhi bemikhumbi ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa.
Tizatfu letincane letibonwako tekutsi kungani lemikhumbi ibuyiswa, kepha bomasiko baseJalimane bacaphuna "tinkinga letibalulekile letitsite letitsite letitsite letitsite" letitsite letitsite "letitsite letitsite letitsite" letenta lemikhumbi ingasebenti kahle uma isetjentiswa etimphini.
Lenkinga ye-software ibaluleke kakhulu ngobe imikhumbi ye-Baden-Wuerttemberg itawusetjentiswa ngemalunga emkhumbi langu-120 - lokusho kutsi, cishe kuhhafu wemalunga emkhumbi wemkhumbi we-Bremen.
Bekwatiwa nekutsi sisindvo salomkhumbi besingaba sincane kakhulu, lokwenta kutsi singabi nemandla futsi kungenta kutsi uMkhumbi ungakhoni kwenta lokunye.
Lelisu leliphakeme kakhulu, lelingemathani langu-7.000, lelibitwa ngekutsi yi-Rheinland-Pfalz, bekukholelwa kutsi linesisindvo lesiphindvwe kabili kunesicumbi semikhumbi lefanako lebeyisetjentiswa ngemaJalimane eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Ngetulu kwekonakala kwetintfo letisetjentiswako, tindleko tekukhicita lomsebenti wonkhe - lokufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti - nako kwaba yinkinga.
Kutsiwa kukhuphuke kakhulu kuya ku-€3.1 billion - kusuka ku-€2.2 billion.
Lenkinga yekubamba lomkhumbi lomusha we-patrol iba yintfo lebaluleke kakhulu ngenca yeticwayiso tekwehla kwemandla emikhumbi yaseJalimane.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, loyinhloko yelikomidi lekuvikela lephalamende yaseJalimane, wavuma kutsi vele liTiko Letaselwandle "lisengakaphelelwa ngemikhumbi yekuhambisa".
Lesisebenti satsi lenkinga iyachubeka ikhula njengobe tikebhe letindzala setingasasebenti futsi kute letinye letitfolakalako.
Watsandza kutsi kube khona umkhumbi lotawuhlanganiswa nemkhumbi wakhe.
I-National Trust ilalele imfihlo yemphilo yaloluhlata ngekuthula
Lucwaningo lolusha lolwentiwe endzaweni yaseScotland Highveld, luhlose kubona kutsi tilwane letingumkhomo tisisebentisa njani indzawo yato kute titfole kudla.
Kucatjangwa kutsi lokutfolwe kutawuniketa kucaciseka lokusha mayelana nendlela letigogo letindizako letitiphatsa ngayo futsi kusite ekucondziseni umsebenti wekulondvolota esikhatsini lesitako.
Lolucwaningo lolwentiwe bososayensi baseNational Trust for Scotland, lutawulandzela ema-pipristrelle kanye nema-soprans lasemkhatsini kanye nema-batfish lanetindlebe letindze kanye nema-daubenton ase-Inverewe Gardens leseWester Ross.
Tintfo tekubhala letitsite titawufakwa etindzaweni letisembili letitungelete lendzawo kute kulandzelwe umsebenti wemalulwane ngesikhatsi semnyaka.
Basebenti be-NHS kanye netisebenti letivolontiya batawuphindze bahlole ngetindzawo tekuhlala basebentisa tintfo tekutfola tintfo.
Sati setindlebe lesatihlatiya tonkhe letindzaba sitakwati kubona kutsi lomkhovu ukhala kangaki nekutsi nguyiphi inhlobo leyentako.
Ngemuva kwaloko emabalave nemibiko yetindzawo tekuhlala kutawakhiwa kwentela kwakha titfombe letinkhulu temvelo letichaza indlela letiphila ngayo.
Rob Dewar, longumeluleki wetendzawo ku-NTS, unethemba lekutsi lomphumela utawukhombisa kutsi nguyiphi indzawo yekuhlala lebaluleke kakhulu kubologwaja nekutsi tilwane letitsite tiyisebentisa njani.
Lolwati lutakusita kutsi ubone kutsi yini longayitfola ngemsebenti wekunakekela tindzawo tekuhlala njengekwakha tindzawo tekuhlanyela kanye nendlela lencono yekugcina tihlahla temalulwane kanye naletinye tilwane letihlobene nato.
Linani lemabhungane eScotland naseNgilandi lonkhe lehle kakhulu kuleminyaka lembalwa leyendlulile.
Lamagwababa asongelwa umsebenti wekwakha kanye nekutfutfukisa lokutsintsa indzawo yawo yekuhlala kanye nekulahlekelwa yindzawo yekuhlala.
Imibhobho yemoya kanye nekukhanyisa nako kunetingoti, njengekuhlanganiswa kweliphepha lelimanyatela kute kubambeke tilwane letihlala emakhaya, kuhlantwa kwetintfo tekwakha, kanye nekuhlaselwa ngemakati.
Ecinisweni, labologwaja ababoni.
Kodvwa ngenca yekutsi titingela ebusuku, tindlebe tato tisebenta kancono kunemehlo ato ekudzingeni kudla.
Basebentisa tindlela tekutfola tigidzi tetinambuzane kute batfole tilwanyana letincane kanye netintfo letingabavimbela kutsi bangaphumeleli.
I-NTS, lenemsebenti wekunakekela takhiwo temlandvo letingetulu kwa-270, tivakashi letibalulekile letingu-38, kanye nemhlaba longemakhilomitha langu-76 000 kulo lonkhe lelive, iyikhatsalela kakhulu iminenkhe.
Bekuba netisebenti letilishumi leticeceshiwe, lebetenta luhlolo, luhlolo lwendzawo yekuhlanganela, kanye nemitamo yekusindzisa.
LeNhlangano iphindze yasungula indzawo yekuvikela imvelo yekucala futsi leyodvwa eScotland eThreave Plantation lese Dumfries nase Galloway, lekungiyo likhaya letinhlobo letisiphohlongo kuletilishumi tetimfene eScotland.
Umphatsi walendzawo, David Thompson, utsi lendzawo iyindzawo lekahle yekuhlala tilwane.
"Lapha eThreave, sinendzawo lenhle yemalulwane", washo njalo.
"Sinezakhiwo takadzeni, tihlahla letindzala, netindzawo letinhle.
Nobe kunjalo, kunyenti lesisengakwati ngemalulwane, ngako umsebenti lesitawukwenta lapha nakuletinye tindzawo utasisita sicondze kabanti ngaloko lakudzingako kute aphile".
Ugcizelela kubaluleka kwekuhlola emalulwane ngaphambi kwekwenta umsebenti wekulungisa indzawo, ngobe kungakhatsaliseki kutsi kubhujiswa kwesidleke sinye sekutala kungabulala tilwane letinsikati letingu-400 kanye naletincane, lokungaba kubulala bonkhe bantfu bendzawo.
Labalwanyana bavikelekile futsi kubulala, kuhlukubeta, kuphatamisa nobe kubulala tindlu tabo kuphambene nemtsetfo.
Elisabeth Ferrell, siphatsimandla saseScotland se-Bat Conservation Trust, ukhutsate bantfu kutsi basite.
Utsi: "Kusekuningi lokusamele sikufundze ngemalulwane etfu kanye netinhlobo letinyenti tetilwane lesisengakati kutsi tiphi".
Ronaldo lowala kutsi wadlwengulwa, ulungiselela kutsi ummeli wakhe amemetele licala lakhe kumagazini waseJalimane
Cristiano Ronaldo ubita kutsi kungena kwakhe "tindzaba letingemanga", futsi utsi bantfu "bafuna kutiphromotha" basebentisa ligama lakhe.
Bameli bakhe batawumangalela bomagazini waseJalimane i-Der Spiegel, lowakhipha lamacala.
Lomgadli wasePortugal kanye neJuventus usolwa ngekudlwengula umfati waseMelika, Kathryn Mayorga, ekamelweni lehhotela laseLas Vegas nga-2009.
Ngemuva kwaloko, wabhadala ngekumnika $375,000 kute angasho lutfo ngalendzaba, Der Spiegel ibika ngaLesihlanu.
Akhuluma ku-Instagram Live video kubalandeli bakhe labatigidzi leti-142, emahora lambalwa ngemuva kwekubikwa kwalombiko, Ronaldo, loneminyaka lengu-33 budzala, walahla lombiko ngekutsi "tinganekwane".
"Cha, cha, cha, cha.
Loku labakusho lamuhla kungumbiko longemanga", lomncobi weBallon d'Or wabatjela loko ngekhatsi ekhamera.
"Bafuna kutisebentisa ngekutisebentisa.
Loko kuyintfo levamile.
Bekafuna kwatiwa ngekukhuluma ngelibito lami, kodvwa loko bekulite.
Ngingumuntfu lojabulako futsi konkhe kuhamba kahle", lomdlali wachubeka amoyitela.
Bameli baRonaldo balungiselela kumangalela iDer Spiegel ngaletinsolo, labatsi "kubika lokungafanele mayelana nekuba nelingasese", ngekusho kwe-Reuters.
Ummeli wakhe, Christian Schertz, watsi utawucela sincephetelo "njengekuhlawulwa lokukhulu lokulingana nebubi baloko lokwentiwe, lokungulokubi kakhulu lokwentiwe eminyakeni lembalwa leyendlulile".
Lesento lesitsintfwa njengalokuyintfo leyenteka ngaJuni 2009 egumbini lelihle lase Palms Hotel and Casino eLas Vegas.
Ngemuva kwekuhlangana enkhundleni yetemidlalo, Ronaldo na Mayorga babuyela ekamelweni lalomdlali, lapho bekutsiwa wamdlwengula khona, ngekusho kwemibiko leyetfulwe eNkantolo yase Clark County eNevada.
Mayorga watsi Ronaldo waguca ngemuva kwesehlakalo lebekabekwe sona wase uyamtjela kutsi "99%" "ungumuntfu lomuhle" lowadumaza "linye%".
Lemiculu itsi Ronaldo uyavuma kutsi bobabili bebalala ndzawonye, kodvwa loko bekusekelwe esifisweni sabo lesifanako.
Mayorga waphindze watsi waya emaphoyiseni futsi wahlolwa tifo takhe esibhedlela, kodvwa wavuma kucedza lenkinga ngaphandle kwenkantolo ngobe "bekesaba kuphindzisela" futsi bekesaba "kuhlazeka embikwebantfu".
Lomfati loneminyaka lengu-34 budzala utsi nyalo ufuna kucedza lesincumo sekuthula ngobe usolo eva buhlungu ngalokwenteka.
Ronaldo besekavele ahambe eManchester United waya eReal Madrid ngesikhatsi kuhlasela kutfolakala, futsi kulenyanga yehlobo watfutsela e-Italy e-Juve ngesivumelwano semali lengemarandi latigidzi letilikhulu.
Brexit: I-UK 'itawulila phakadze' ngekulahlekelwa yincenye yemkhicito wemoto
I-UK "itawuzisola phakadze" uma ilahlekelwa simo sayo sekuba ngumholi wemhlaba wekukhicita timoto ngemuva kwe-Brexit, kusho iNdvuna yeTemabhizinisi Greg Clark.
Wengeta watsi "mayelana" neToyota, iBrithani itjele iBBC kutsi uma iBrithani iphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, itawumisa kwesikhashana kukhicitwa kwayo eBurnaston, dvutane neDerby.
"Sidzinga sivumelwano", kwasho Mnu. Clark.
Umkhicito wemoto waseJapan utsi umtselela wekubambezeleka kwemincele uma kungekho sivumelwano, utawuba mubi nge-Brexit ngekwemali yekusebenta.
Lesakhiwo saseBurnaston - lesenta i-Auris ne-Avensis yekukhicita i-Toyota - sakhicita cishe timoto letingu-150,000 emnyakeni lowengcile, lokungaba ngu-90% wato letatfunyelwa e-Europe.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma i-UK iphuma e-EU ekupheleni kwa-March, sitawuyibona imisa umkhicito etitolo tetfu", kusho Marvin Cooke, longumcondzisi lophetse we-Toyota eBurnaston.
Labanye bakhiciti betimoto baseBrithani bakhulume ngekukhatsateka kwabo ngekuphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano sekutsi kutsengiselana kwemincele kutawuhamba njani, lokufaka ekhatsi iHonda, iBMW, neJaguar Land Rover.
I-BMW, sibonelo, itsi itawuvala ifektri yayo ye-Mini e-Oxford tinyanga letimbalwa ngemuva kwe-Brexit.
Inkinga lenkhulu lehlobene naloko lokushiwo bakhiciti betimoto kutsi kunengoti yekuphakela ngaphandle kwekutfola sivumelwano se-Brexit.
Umklamo weToyota usebenta ngekulandzela umgomo wekukhicita "ngesikhatsi", netincenye letitfolakala njalo ngemizuzu lengu-37 kusuka kumphakeli wase-UK kanye nase-EU kute kube netimoto letentiwe ngendlela.
Nangabe i-UK iphuma e-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ngaMashi 29, kutawuba nekuphazamiseka emnceleni, lokusho kutsi imboni ingahle iholele ekubambekeni nasekushodeni kwetingcezu.
Kutakwenta kube matima kutsi iToyota igcine timphahla tayo emapulazini ayo aseDerbyshire sikhatsi lesingaba lilanga, kusho ummeleli wayo, futsi loko kutawuvimbela kukhicitwa.
Clark watsi luhlelo lwa Theresa May lwe Chequers lwekusebentisana ne EU esikhatsini lesitako "luhlolwe kahle kute kugwenywe kuhlolwa eminyeleni".
"Kufanele sivumelane. Sifuna kutfola sivumelwano lesincono kakhulu lesitawuphindze sivumele loko lengikushoko kutsi kungabi nje kuphela kutfola imphumelelo nyalo, kepha kutsi sitfole ematfuba", washo kuloluhlelo lwe-BBC Radio 4's Today.
"Loku kufakazela kutsi akusiko nje iToyota kuphela kepha nalabanye bakhiciti, kutsi kufanele siciniseke kutsi siyakhona kuchubeka naloko lesekuvele kuyindlela yekuphakela lesekwenteke kahle".
I-Toyota ayikhoni kusho kutsi itawuvala sikhatsi lesingakanani, kepha kucacile kutsi kutawuba sikhatsi lesidze, icwayisa ngekutsi kukhuphuka kwetindleko kutawucedza kuchudzelana kwetimboni futsi ekugcineni kutawuba kubi kakhulu ngetindleko tebasebenti.
Peter Tsouvallaris, losebente eBurnaston iminyaka lengu-24 futsi lowengamele inyunyana ye-UNITE, utsi emalunga ayo sekakhatsatekile: "Kwetifundvo tami, nangabe lomsebenti sewuphelile, angeke uphindze ubuye.
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: "Sifake luhlelo loluhle nalolunengcondvo lwetinhlelo tetfu tebudlelwane ne-EU esikhatsini lesitako".
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein kungenteka uphindze uhlehliswe, kusho iWhite House
Umhlangano lobeka ingoti kakhulu wa Donald Trump neLisekela Lemmeli Lomkhulu Rod Rosenstein "ungahlehliselwa emuva liviki" njengoba kulwa kwemuntfu lotawuba ngumengameli wenkantolo lephakeme Brett Kavanaugh kusachubeka, kusho iWhite House ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein bekangamele umsebenti wemeluleki lowehlukile Robert Mueller, lobekaphenya ngekungenelela kweRussia elukhetfweni, budlelwane emkhatsini webasiti baTrump kanye neRussia, kanye nekungenelela kwebaholi benkantolo.
Kungabe Trump utawucosha ummeli lomkhulu nobe cha, lokutawubeka engotini inkhululeko yaMueller, sekube yintfo lebeyitsatselwa etulu eWashington tinyanga letinyenti.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, iNew York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein bekakhuluma ngekusebentisa umlayeto kute abhale inkhulumo yakhe naTrump kanye nekususa umengameli ngekusebentisa luchibiyelo lwesi-25.
Rosenstein waphika lombiko.
Kodvwa ngeMsombuluko lowengcile waya eWhite House, ngesikhatsi sekuvakaliswa kutsi utawushiya sikhundla sakhe.
Esikhundleni saloko, umhlangano naTrump, lobekahlala ehhovisi le-UN eNew York, wamenyetelwa ngeLesine.
Trump watsi "utawukhetsa kunga" khishwa Rosenstein, kepha lomhlangano wabuye wahlehliswa kute kugwenywe kungcubutana nelikomidi lesigungu seSenate lebugebengu lapho khona Kavanaugh nalomunye walabasikati labambeka licala lekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, Dokotela Christine Blasey Ford, bobabili batawufakaza.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wayala kutsi i-FBI iphenye ngekuhlaselwa kwaKavanaugh liviki lonkhe, lokwaphindze kwavimbela kuvotelwa kweSigungu Lesibusako.
Umshumayeli waTrump, Sarah Sanders, ukhuluma ku-Fox News ngeLisontfo.
Nakabutwa mayelana nemhlangano naRosenstein, watsi: "Lilanga lemhlangano alikasungulwa, kungenteka kutsi kutawuba ngeliviki, futsi ngibona kutsi kuhle kutsi kuhlehliselwe lelinye liviki ngenca yalokunye lokwentekile enkantolo lephakeme.
Kodvwa sitawutibonela nje futsi ngihlale ngifuna kutjela bemitfombo yetindzaba".
Labanye babhali batawuphikisa lombiko: Sanders akazange abambe umhlangano wetindzaba eWhite House kusukela ngaSeptember 10.
Umsakazi wetfu Chris Wallace wabuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders watsi lokuhlangana lokuncane akubangelwa kungatsandzi batati betindzaba teTV "leticedza kuvelela", nanobe, watsi: "Angivumelani nekutsi betama kuvelela".
Ngemuva kwaloko wacela kutsi kube nekuhlangana lokukhulu emkhatsini waTrump kanye nebetindzaba.
"Umengameli wenta imibuto leminyenti kunemengameli wangaphambilini", wachubeka ngaphandle kwekusho bufakazi: "Sesivele siwabonile lamaphuzu".
Umhlangano usetawenteka, kusho Sanders, kepha "uma betindzaba banematfuba ekubuta umengameli waseMelika imibuto matfupha, kuncono kakhulu kunekukhuluma nami.
Senta konkhe lokusemandleni etfu kutsi sikwente kanyenti futsi niyakubona loko lesikwentile kuleminyaka lembalwa leyengcile futsi loko kutawutsatsa sikhundla semhlangano wetindzaba uma ngabe nikhuluma nemengameli waseMelika".
Trump uvame kubuta imibuto nakaphuma eWhite House nobe uma ahlanganyela emhlanganweni nobe emhlanganweni wetindzaba netiphatsimandla letiphakeme letivakashile.
Kungakavami kutsi kube nemhlangano wetindzaba loyedvwa.
Kuleliviki eNew York, Mengameli utawukhombisa kutsi kungani, ente tintfo letingacondzakali futsi ngalesinye sikhatsi letimangalisako ngaphambi kwekutsi betindzaba bahlangane.
Umcondzisi weTemphilo ubhalele basebenti base-EU ku-NHS yaseScotland ngekukhatsateka nge-Brexit
Mabhalane wetemphilo ubhalele basebenti base-EU labasebenta ku-NHS Scotland ngekubonga live labo futsi uncenga kutsi bachubeke basebente lapha ngemuva kwetinkinga te-Brexit.
Jeane Freeman, longumuntfu lolilunga lephalamende, watfumela incwadzi ngesikhatsi lesingaphasi kwetinyanga letisitfupha ngaphambi kwekutsi iBrithani ishiye i-European Union.
Hulumende waseScotland utibophezele ekutseni abambe tindleko tekufaka sicelo sekuba semtsetfweni kubantfu base-EU labasebenta emisebentini yahulumende labajikisiwe.
Encwadzini yakhe, Ms. Freeman wabhala: "Kulelihlobo, tinkhulumiswano emkhatsini weBrithani ne-EU mayelana nekuphuma kwelive laleli tichubeka, tisondzela esiphetfweni lesilindzeleke kulenyanga yeMphala.
Kodvwa hulumende waseBrithani naye bekakulungele kubukana nesimo sekungaboni ngaso linye.
Ngiyati kutsi loku kufanele kube kuyintfo lebuhlungu kakhulu kini nonkhe.
Kungako-ke nyalo ngifuna kuphindze ngivume kutsi ngiyawutsandza kakhulu umnikelo webasebenti, kungakhatsaliseki kutsi bavela kuliphi live.
Bozakwethu labavela kulo lonkhe laseYurophu, kanye nalabanye, baletsa lwati lolubalulekile kanye nemakhono lacinisa aphindze ente ncono umsebenti wetemphilo, futsi kuzuzisa tigulane kanye nemiphakatsi lesiyisebentisako.
IScotland likhaya lakho futsi sifuna uhlale khona".
Christion Abercrombie Wenta Luhlolo Lwesimo Lesiphutfumako Ngemuva Kwekulimala Enhloko
Umdlali we Tennessee State Tigers Christion Abercrombie wahlinzwa ngekushesha ngemuva kwekugula enhloko ekulahlekelweni ngu 31-27 yi Vanderbilt Commodores ngeMgcibelo, kusho Mike Organ wase Tennessee.
Umceceshi we Tennessee Rod Reed watjela batsebuli kutsi lokulimala kwakhe kwenteka ngaphambi nje kwekutsi umdlalo uphele.
"Wafika eceleni kwalendzawo futsi wafela khona lapho", kusho Reed.
Baceceshi kanye netisebenti tetemphilo banika Abercrombie umoya longcolile ngasekugcineni kwendzawo ngaphambi kwekutsi bamfake etaleni futsi bamtfwale kute aphindze ahlolwe.
Siphatsimandla saseTennessee satjela Chris Harris we-WSMV eNashville, Tennessee, kutsi Abercrombie uphumile egumbini lekuhlinza eVanderbilt Medical Center.
Harris wachubeka watsi "kusete imininingwane mayelana neluhlobo/nelizinga lalokulimala" futsi Sifundza saseTennessee sifuna kwati kutsi lokulimala kwenteka nini.
Abercrombie, umfundzi wesibili lobuke libhande lelibovu, usemnyakeni wakhe wekucala neTennessee State ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa e-Illinois.
Wafaka ema-tackles lasihlanu ngaMgcibelo ngaphambi kwekutsi aphume emdlalweni, lokwenta kutsi aphelele ekubambeni ema-tackles langu-18 kulomnyaka.
Batsengi betive batawukhokhiswa imali lenyenti yekubhala uma batsenga imphahla yaseNgilandi
Batsengi labachamuka emaveni angaphandle batawukhokhiswa imali lenyenti yekubhala uma batsenga indzawo eNgilandi, kanye nemali lengetiwe letawusetjentiswa ekusiteni bantfu labangenamakhaya ngaphasi kweluhlelo lolusha lwemaTory
Loku kutawuvimbela inchubo yeCorbyn yekuhlanganisa bantfu labasha.
Lokwenyuswa kwetimali tekubhala kutawuba semahlombe alabo labangakhokhi umtselo eNgilandi.
Litiko Letetimali licabanga kutsi kutawucitfwa tigidzi temarandi letingu-120 ngemnyaka kute kusitwe bantfu labangenamakhaya.
Batsengi bangaphandle batawukhokhiswa imali lenyenti yekubekwa sitembu uma batsenga tindlu eNgilandi - kanye nemali lengetiwe letawusetjentiswa ekusiteni bantfu labangenamakhaya, Theresa May utawumemetela loku lamuhla.
Loku kutawubonakala njengentfo yekubamba umfutfo wemitamo yaJeremy Corbyn yekudvonsela bantfu labasha ngekubatsembisa tindlu letingabizi kakhulu kanye nekuhlela imali lenyenti.
Kunetindleko letinkhulu tekubhala kubantfu kanye netinkampani letingabhadali umtselo eNgilandi, kanye nemali lengetiwe leyenta kutsi hulumende alwe nekuhlukunyetwa kwebantfu labahlala bangenamakhaya.
Tindleko letengetiwe - letitindleko letengetiwe letitfolakala ngetindleko tekubhalisa letikhona nyalo, lokufaka ekhatsi emazinga lasetulu lasungulwa eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile ekutsengeni indlu yesibili kanye nekutsenga indlu yekucasha - tingangena emaphesentheni lamatsatfu.
Litiko Letetimali licabanga kutsi loku kutawunyuka kube ngu-£120 million ngemnyaka.
Kulinganiselwa kutsi emaphesenti langu-13 etakhiwo letinsha letakhiwa eLondon atsengwa bantfu labangasibo baseBrithani, lokwenta kutsi intsengo inyuke futsi kwente kube matima ngemtsengi wekucala kutsi angene etindlini.
Tindzawo letinyenti leticebile kulelive - ikakhulukati enhloko-dolobha - setigcine sekuti "madolobha latingoti" ngenca yebantfu labanyenti lababuya emaveni angaphandle labatosebenta emaveni angaphandle.
Lenchubomgomo lensha iphuma ngemuva kweliviki Boris Johnson afune kuncishiswa kwetindleko tekubhala kute kusitwe bantfu labasha kutsi babe nemakhaya abo ekucala.
Wasola tinkampani letinkhulu tekwakha kutsi tigcina intsengo yetindlu iphezulu ngekutsenga umhlaba kepha tingawusebentisi, waphindze wakhutsata May kutsi angatinaki timfuneko tetindlu letingabizi kute alungise "sifo sekuhlala" eNgilandi.
Corbyn umemetele luhlu lwetinhlelo tekugucula etindzaweni tekuhlala, kufaka ekhatsi kubuka tindlu tekuhlala kanye nekucedza kucoshwa "ngekungati".
Waphindze wafuna kuniketa Sigungu saVelonkhe emandla lamakhulu ekwakha tindlu letinsha.
May watsi: "Ngemnyaka lowengcile ngetsembisa kutsi ngitawutinikela emsebentini wami wekuba nguNdvunankhulu kute ngibuyisele liphupho laseBrithani - lekutsi imphilo kufanele ibe ncono kuto tonkhe titukulwane.
Loko kusho kulungisa imakethe yetindlu yetfu lephukile.
I-United Kingdom itawuhlala ivulekele bonkhe labafuna kuhlala, kusebenta nekwakha imphilo yabo lapha.
Nobe kunjalo, akukafaneli kutsi bantfu labangakemi e-UK, kanye netinkampani letisebenta emaveni angaphandle, batsenge tindlu ngendlela bantfu base-UK labatiphatsa ngayo.
Bantfu labanyenti baphelelwa ngemandla ekutsi babe nemakhaya abo, futsi kuphatfwa kabi kwebabaleki solo kuyintfo levamile".
Jack Ross: 'Umgomo wami lomkhulu kuhola licembu laseScotland'
Umcondzisi we Sunderland, Jack Ross utsi "sifiso sakhe lesikhulu" kuba ngumphatsi wase Scotland ngetikhatsi letitsite.
Lomdlali waseScotland, loneminyaka lengu-42, ujabulela kuvivinywa kwekuvuselela licembu laseNyakatfo-mpumalanga, lelisesikhundleni sesitsatfu kuLigi Lokuqala, ngekwehluka ngemaphuzu lamatsatfu kusuka ekucaleni.
Waya e Stadium of Light ehlobo ngemuva kwekucinisa iSt Mirren ibuyele eScotland Premier League kulomnyaka lophelile.
"Ngifuna kumelela live lami njengemdlali.
Ngatfola umchele we-B futsi nguloko", Ross watjela i-Sportsound, i-BBC Scotland.
"Kodvwa ngakhula futsi bengivame kubukela licembu laseScotland eHampden nababe wami ngisemncane, futsi bekuhlala kungenta ngifune kubuyela emuva.
Kodvwa-ke, litfuba litawufika, nangabe ngiphumelela ekulawuleni licembu".
Bacondzisi be Sunderland ngaphambi kwa Ross bafaka ekhatsi Dick Advocaat, David Moyes, Sam Allardyce, Martin O'Neill, Roy Keane, Gus Poyet, kanye na Paulo Di Canio.
Lobeyisikhulu se-Alloa Athletic utsi akesabi kulandzela emagama lamakhulu kulelicembu lelikhulu kangaka, ngemuva kwekwala kuniketwa ngu-Barnsley ne-Ipswich Town.
"Kimi, imphumelelo yami nyalo itawulinganiswa ngekutsi 'ngingayibuyisela yini lelicembu ePremier League?'
Ngenca yetakhiwo netintfo letikhona kulelicembu, kute kungaba khona kungabata kutsi kutawuba khona ePremier League", kusho yena.
"Kute umsebenti lomelula kutsi ube khona, kodvwa mhlawumbe ngitawutibona ngingumuntfu lophumelele lapha, nangabe ngingabuyisa lelicembu".
Umsebenti wa Ross wekuphatsa licembu waba yiminyaka lemitsatfu kuphela, ngemuva kwesikhatsi lesitsite sekuba ngumsizi wemholi eDumbarton, wase ucitsa tinyanga letilishumi nesihlanu angumceceshi welicembu lase Hearts.
Ngemuva kwaloko wasita Alloa kutsi alulame ekuhlushweni aye endzaweni yesitsatfu, waphindze wagucula iSt Mirren kusuka ekuhlushweni kuya ekuwineni umchele welibhola letinyawo ngesikhatsi lesilandzelako.
Ross utsi utiva akhululekile kakhulu kunakucala ngesikhatsi adlala e-Clyde, Hartlepool, Falkirk, St Mirren, nase-Hamilton Academical.
"Lena kungaba yindzawo lengifanele ngiyidlule", wakhumbula nakatsatsa sikhundla sa-Alloa.
"Bengikholwa kutsi kuphatsa ngiko lokulungile kimi, kunekudlala.
Loko kuvakala kungakavami ngobe bengiphila imphilo lentofontofo, ngiphila ngendlela lekahle futsi ngikujabulela kakhulu kwenta tintfo letivamile.
Kodvwa kudlala kungaba matima.
Kunetintfo letinyenti lokufanele utibekele tona liviki ngalinye.
Ngisachubeka nekubhekana nekucindzetelwa ngumsebenti, kodvwa ekulawuleni ngitiva kahle.
Bengisolo ngifuna kuba ngumholi futsi nyalo sengiyamhola, lokuyintfo lengiyitsandzako lengingazange ngiyente ekuphileni kwami".
Ungamuva ngalokuphelele ku-Sportsound ngeLisontfo, Septhemba 30, ku-Radio Scotland emkhatsini wa-12:00 na-1:00 BST
Luhlolo lutfole kutsi sikhatsi lesikahle sekunatsa libhiya ngu-5:30 ntsambama ngeMgcibelo.
Kushisa kwelihlobo kwenyuse imali yetitolo tase-UK letisebenta kamatima, kepha kwengeta umfutfo etinhlelweni tetitolo.
Tinombolo tikhombisa kutsi emacembu etitolo kanye netibaya abona kukhula lokungu-2.7% ekutsengisweni ngaJulayi - kodvwa imali letfolwa ngulabo labadla etindzaweni tekudlela yehle nga-4.8%.
Peter Martin, longumeluleki wetemabhizinisi e-CGA, lowabhala letibalo, watsi: "Lilanga lelikhanyako kanye nekubamba lichaza kwe-England eMdlalweni Wemhlaba sikhatsi lesidze kunaloko bekulindzelwe kusho kutsi inyanga yaJuly itawulandzela indlela leyaphindze yabonakala ngenyanga yeNhlaba leyendlulile, lapho imali yetitolo temaphuphu yakhula ngayo ngemaphesenti langu-2.8, ngaphandle kwetitolo letisebentisa tidloli letishaywa kakhulu.
Kwehla kwemali yekutsengisa ngetitolo lokungu-1.8% ngaJuni kutawuba kubi kakhulu ngaJulayi.
Kwengeta lapho, kutsengiswa kwetitolo temanti netinatfo letitsengiswa etindzaweni tekudlela letinetjwala kukhule kakhulu kunekwenyuka kwetitolo letitsengisa kudla.
Tindlu letitsengisa kudla nato tiyahlupheka ngenca yekushisa kwelilanga, nanobe tingabi buhlungu njengalabo labatsengisa kudla.
Kubonakala shengatsi bantfu baphuma bayotsintsana.
Kutsengiswa kwetitolo temanti netinatfo letitsengiswa ngemabhavu kukhuphuke ngamaphesenti langu-6.6 kulenyanga, kantsi kudla kwehle ngemaphesenti lamatsatfu".
Paul Newman, longumhlatiyi wetemidlalo netemahhotela ku-RSM utsi: "Loku kuhlanganisa tintfo lesetentekile kusukela nga-April.
Simo selitulu kanye nemiphumela yetintfo letinkhulu letenteka emmangweni nobe temidlalo kusolo kuyincenye lenkhulu yekutsengiswa kwetitolo tasemakhaya.
Akumangalisi kutsi licembu letindzawo tekudlela lichubeka nekulwa kute lisindze, nanobe kwehla kwemakethe lokungu-4.8 ekhulwini ngemnyaka kutawuba buhlungu kakhulu ngenca yetindleko letisetulu.
Lelishisa kakhulu alifanele lifike ngesikhatsi lapho khona bantfu labatsengisa kudla babhekene netimo letimbi, futsi sikhatsi sitawuveta kutsi simo selitulu lesikahle lesisijabulele nga-August sitawuniketa yini bantfu baphumule".
Kukhula lokugcwele kwekutsengiswa kwetitolo etindzaweni tekudlela kanye netitolo, kufaka ekhatsi letinsha, kwaba ngu 2.7 ekhulwini ngenyanga yeNhlaba, lokukhombisa kuncipha kwekusungula emabhizinisi.
I-Coffer Peach Tracker yekuhlola kutsengisa kwemabhizinisi etitolo, emabhavu kanye netitolo e-UK ihlanganisa iphindze ihlatiye idatha yekusebenta yemacembu langu-47 lasebentako, lanemali lengetulu kwetigidzigidzi letingu-£9 futsi iyindlela yekuhlola lengeke iphikiswe.
Umntfwana munye kulabasihlanu unema-akhawunti langakacondziswa batali bakhe etinhlelweni tekuchumana.
Lucwaningo lukhombisa kutsi umntfwana munye kulabasihlanu - labanye babo labaneminyaka lengu-11 budzala - bane-akhawunti yabo yangasese yekuchumana labayigcina ifihlekile kubatali babo nakubothishela
Luhlolo lolwentiwe kubafundzi labangu-20 000 labasesikolweni lesisetulu lwembula indlela "ema-Insta emanga" lakhula ngayo
Letindzaba tikhulisa kukhatsateka ngekutfunyelwa kwetindzaba letimbi.
Emaphesenti langemashumi lamabili ebafundzi batsi bane-akhawunti "lemcoka" lekumele bayikhombise batali babo
Umntfwana munye kulabasihlanu - labanye babo labaneminyaka lengu-11 budzala - uvula ema-akhawunti akhe ekuchumana labagcina afihlekile kubantfu labadzala.
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe kubafundzi labangu-20 000 labasemabanga lasetulu lwembula kukhula lokukhulu kwema-akhawunti "labangemanga" - lokuyindlela yekuhlanganyela titfombe ku-Instagram.
Letindzaba tikhulisa kukhatsateka ngekutsi utawutfumela tintfo letikhombisa kungcola.
Emaphesenti langu-20 ebafundzi batsi basebentisa ema-akhawunti "labalulekile" labese ayasuswa kute aboniswe batali babo, kantsi baphindze babe nema-akhawunti abo.
Lomunye make watfola i-website yemntfwanakhe loneminyaka lengu-13 budzala, watfola umfana lotsite losemusha locela lomunye umuntfu kutsi "angidlwengule".
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe yi-Digital Awareness yase-UK kanye ne-HMC (Hall of Headmasters and Headmistresses) yetikolo letitimele, litfole kutsi 40 ekhulwini lebafundzi labaneminyaka lengu-11 kuya ku-18 banemaphrofayli lamabili, futsi incenye yabo itsi banemakhasi abo.
Mike Buchanan, longumphatsi we-HMC utsi: "Loku kuyayiphatamisa indlela bantfwana labasebasha labatiphatsa ngayo nabafuna kufinyelela etindzaweni letitfolakala ku-Internet, futsi batali babo nabothishela babo abakwati kutitfola".
Eilidh Doyle utawuba "ligama lalabadlali" emhlanganweni we-Scottish Athletic Council
Eilidh Doyle ukhetfwe kutsi abe ngumcondzisi longasebenti emhlanganweni wemnyaka we-Scotland Athletic.
Doyle ngumdlali we-track and field waseScotland loniketwe umklomelo lomkhulu futsi lomengameli Ian Beattie uchaza loku njengematfuba lamakhulu kulabo labaholako kutemidlalo kutsi bazuze kulokuhlangenwe nako kwakhe lokunyenti emaveni emhlaba kuleminyaka lembalwa leyengcile.
"Eilidh uhlonishwa kakhulu eScotland, eNgilandi, nasemphakatsini wetemidlalo mhlabawonkhe futsi siyakholwa kutsi temidlalo eScotland titawuzuza kakhulu ngekumfaka kuleligumbi", kusho Beattie.
Doyle utsi: "Ngisebenta njengelivi lalabadlali futsi ngifisa kufaka ligalelo futsi ngisite ekuholeni temidlalo eScotland".
Umsubathi waseMelika, lowancoba ema-200 nemamitha langu-400 kuma-Olympic ase-Atlanta nga-1996 emkhatsini wetindondo takhe tegolide letine tema-Olympic futsi nyalo losati se-BBC, nyalo akakwati kuhamba ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa sifo sekushona kwematsambo.
Wabhala kuTwitter watsi: "Lamuhla inyanga leyengcile ngaba nesifo sengcondvo.
Angikwati kuhamba.
Bodokotela batsi sikhatsi kuphela lesitawusho kutsi ngitawuphindze ngibe nemphilo lenjani nekutsi kutawuba njani.
Bekungumsebenti lomatima kakhulu kuphindze utfole emandla, uphindze ufundze kuhamba, futsi lamuhla ngente umsebenti wekuhlakanipha!
Ngiyabonga ngemilayeto yenu lecinisako!"
Sikhangisi semanti ekudvonsa sifuba lesicatsanisa make netinkhomo, sibangele kuhlukana lokukhulu ku-Internet
Inkampani yekupompa emabele yehlukanisa bantfu ku-Internet ngesikhangiso lesicatsanisa make loncelisako nenkhomo leyayigundvwako.
Kute kukhonjiswe kukhululwa kwalomkhicito lokutsiwa "ngumshini wekucala wekupompa emabele longasebenti", inkampani yetekuhweba ngebucwepheshe i-Elvie yakhipha sikhangisi lesakhutsatwa ngemavidiyo emculo lamnandzi kute ikhombise inkhululeko lekhishwa ngulomshini lomusha wekupompa emabele kute umake ative.
Bomake labane bebadlala esibayeni lesatigcwele tjani betinkhomo, bahlabela ingoma lebeyinemavi lafana nalawa: "Yebo, ngiyabhidlika, kodvwa awuboni umsila wami" kanye na "Nangabe ungakunakanga loku, akusiko umsila wami, butsanga bami".
Wachubeka watsi: "Pump out, pump out, I feed them baby, pump out, pump out, I red my woman's milk".
Nanobe kunjalo, sikhangiso lesishicilelwe ekhasini lale-Facebook, sibangele kuphikisana ku-intanethi.
Ngekubukwa lokungaba ngu-77 000 kanye nemakhulu etimphendvulo, le-video itfole timphendvulo letehlukene kubantfu, labanyenti batsi yenta "lusizi" embonini yetelubisi.
"Kwaba sincumo lesibi kakhulu kusebentisa tinkhomo kute kukhangiswe ngalomkhicito.
Njengatsi, tinkhomo kufanele tikhulelwe futsi titsele kute tikhicite lubisi, ngaphandle nangabe bantfwana bato bayatsatfwa emalangeni lambalwa ngemuva kwekutala", kubhala lomunye umuntfu.
Umpompi wa-Elvie welicandza ufaka kahle kakhulu emabhulukweni.
Lomunye utsi: "Kuhlukunyetwa lokucondzakalako kuyasita kumake nakubantfwana.
Kodvwa-ke, kungani ungakasebentisi loku kute ukhangise ngemapayipi ekudzambisa emabele kubomake labanakekela bantfwana babo?"
Lomunye wachubeka watsi: "Sikhangiso lesingasho lutfo".
Labanye bantfu bayivikela le-advert, lomunye umfati watsi wayitfola "ihlekisa".
"Ngicabanga kutsi ngumbono lomuhle kakhulu.
Bengitawuyitsenga nangisolo ngisebeletsisa.
Kucindzetela kungenta ngitive senginjengenkomo.
Bekungatsiwa ngumkhangiso longenangcondvo, kodvwa ngawemukela.
Lomkhicito uyincenye yekuhlakanipha", kwabhala lomunye.
Lomunye watsi: "Lena yimikhangiso lejabulisako lebhalelwe bomake labatigcabhako (lokuvame kuba semsebentini nobe endlini yangasese) futsi labatitfola 'banjengetinkhomo.'
Akusiko kukhangisa lokuncoma nobe lokwehlulela imboni yetelubisi".
Ekugcineni kwale-video, licembu lebantfu labasikati liveta kutsi bonkhe beva shengatsi bayadansa nemanti afihliwe lafihlwe ngaphansi kwemabhulukwe abo.
Umklamo wekukhankasela lomkhankaso wasungulwa ngekubona kwalabantfu labasikati labanyenti labakhokha lubisi, labatsi bativa banjengetinkhomo.
Kodvwa-ke, i-Elvie Pump yayithule, ite tintambo nobe ema-tubes futsi ifakwe ngaphakathi kwe-bra yekumunyisa, lokwavumela bomake kutsi bakhone kuhamba, bagone bantfwana babo, futsi baphindze baphume bangakashayi.
Ana Balarin, longumlingani kanye na-ECD kuMake utsi: "I-Elvie Pump ingumkhicito loyinhloko lofanele kutsi usungulwe ngendlela lecinisekisako nalevusa inkhanuko.
Ngekuhlanganisa umfanekiso wemfati loveta luvo lwakhe nemkhomo lonatsako sifuna kukhipha lubisi kanye nato tonkhe tinkinga talo, futsi sikukhombise ngendlela lejabulisako nalenenkhululeko lenkhulu leniketwa ngumpompi lomusha.
Loku akusiko kwekucala kutsi ipompo ya-Elvie ibe setfunjini.
NgeLiviki Lemfashini LaseLondon, make webantfwana lababili wabukela umklami Marta Jakubowski asebentisa lomkhicito.
Emakhulu Ebantfwana Labakhoseli Aphambukela Emathendeni Emngceleni WaseTexas
Linani lebantfwana labatfunjiwe liyakhula nanobe kuwela umncele njalo ngenyanga kungagucuki, lokubangelwa kucinisa kanye nemitsetfo leyentiwe hulumende waTrump leyenta kube matima kukhulisa bantfwana labanabo.
Ngalokuyinhloko, labanyenti balabo lababasekelako batakhamuti letingenabo emalungelo, futsi besaba kulimata likhono labo lekuhlala kulelive ngekutfutfukisa kusindzisa bantfwana.
Ingoti yakhula ngaJuni, ngesikhatsi hulumende wasekhaya amemetela kutsi labo labafuna kuba ngubanikeli kanye nalabanye bantfu labadzala emakhaya abo batawudzinga kuniketa iminwe yabo, futsi lemininingwane itawuphindze yabelwe hulumende wetekufika.
Ngeliviki leliphelile, Matthew Albence, sisebenti lesiphakeme se-Immigration and Customs Enforcement, wafakaza embikwalelive kutsi le-ejensi ibophe bantfu labanyenti lebebafaka ticelo tekusekela bantfwana labasebancane.
Luphiko lwacinisekisa kutsi emaphesenti langu-70 alabo lababoshiwe abete emacala.
"Licishe libe ngemaphesenti langu-80 lebantfu labaceceshwako nobe emalunga etinhlangano leticeceshwako labakhona kulelive ngalokungekho emtsetfweni, futsi linyenti labo bantfu lababi labangephandle.
Kungako sichubeka nekubafuna", kwasho Mnumzane Albence.
Kute basheshe bacoce ngalomntfwana, tiphatsimandla setfula umtsetfo lomusha lofuna kutsi labanye babo bete enkantolo kungakapheli inyanga baboshiwe, kunekutsi babe khona ngemuva kwemalanga langu-60, njengobe bekungumkhuba, kusho tisebenti tasendlini yekukhosela.
Labanyenti babo bebakhuluma ngelucingo lwekuhlangana nge-video, hhayi ngekubonana, kute bafake ticelo tabo tekuvunyelwa kuba semtsetfweni kumantji wetekufika.
Labo labangafunwa kutsi basite bantfu labatsite batawususwa.
Njengobe bantfwana bagcinwa sikhatsi lesidze, kungenteka kutsi bakhatsateke kakhulu nobe bacindzeteleke, lokubangele kutsi kube nekukhula kweludlame nobe kwetama kubaleka, kusho tisebenti tasendlini yekukhosela kanye nemibiko leyetfulwe ngulenchubo etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile.
Bameli batsi kukhatsateka kukhula etindzaweni letinkhulu letifana neTornillo, lapho khona timphawu temntfwana lohluphekako tingabukelwa phansi ngenca yebukhulu bakhe.
Batsi kutfutsa bantfwana baye emadolobheni emakhempu ngaphandle kwekubaniketa sikhatsi lesenele sekubasita kutsi bative kahle nobe sekubavalelisa bangani babo, kungabangela buhlungu lobukhulu.
ISyria icela 'emabutfo ekuhlasela' aseMelika, eFrance naseTurkey kutsi ahambe ngekushesha
Akhuluma eMhlanganweni Wetive Wemave Emhlaba, iNdvuna Yetelive Walid al-Moualem wacela kutsi bakhoseli baseSiriya babuyele emakhaya abo, nanobe imphi yaseSiriya nyalo seyingena emnyakeni wayo wesiphohlongo.
