Nati letinye tetindzawo letinezivunguvungu temhlaba letinkhulu letenteke kuleminyaka lembalwa leyendlulile:
NgaDecember 26, 2004, kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwashaya i-Indonesia, lokuyintfo leyenteka elugwini lwasenshonalanga ye-Aceh, enyakatfo yeSumatra, futsi kwabangela ema-tsunami emaveni langu-14, kwabulala bantfu labangu-226,000 ngaselugwini loluselugwini lwe-Indian Ocean, futsi bantfu labangetulu kwesigamu labashona bavela e-Aceh.
2005: Ngasekupheleni kwaMarch nasekucaleni kwa-April, kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokushaya lusentse lolusentshonalanga yeSumatra.
Esihlengeni saseNias, lesingaselugwini lwaseSumatra, kwafa bantfu labanyenti.
2006: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla langu-6.8 kuhlasela eningizimu yeJava, sihlenge lesinebantfu labanyenti e-Indonesia, kwabangela kutsi kube neluswatfu lolubhubhisako lolwaselugwini loluseningizimu futsi kwabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-700.
Nga-2009: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.6 kwenteka edolobheni lasePadang, enhloko-dolobha yesifundza saseWest Sumatra.
Bantfu labafa bahlanganisa bantfu labangetulu kwa-1 100.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokungu-7.5 lokwenteka esihlengeni saseMentawai, lesingaselugwini lwaseSumatra, kwabangela tsunami lephakeme ngemamitha langu-10 budze, lokwacekela phansi imiphakatsi leminyenti futsi kwabulala bantfu labangaba ngu-300.
Nga-2016: Sifundza sasePidie Jaya, e-Aceh, saphindze sabhekana nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwabhubhisa bantfu labanyenti, futsi kwenteka tintfo letinyenti letatigubha bantfu.
Nanobe kungeke kube ne-tsunami, kodvwa bantfu labangetulu kwa-100 bafa ngenca yekubhidlika kwalesakhiwo.
Nga-2018: Lombok, leyatsiwa siqhingi setivakashi, yaphindze yaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, labanyenti babo basenyakatfo yalesichingi.
Lokuzamazama kwemhlaba kwabhidlita takhiwo letinkhulungwane futsi kwabulala netivakashi letinkhulungwane.
