Palin ubhekene netinhlawulo letintsatfu telicembu A, letingaholela ekuvalelweni umnyaka munye kanye netinhlawulo letingu-$250,000.
Ngetulu kwaloko, naye ubekwe licala lelicembu B, lelisigwebo sakhe lilanga linye ejele kanye nenhlawulo lengu-$2,000.
