Andrea Jenkyns, longumholi we-Tory Brexiteer lowahamba nalesicheme, watjela batsebuli betindzaba watsi: 'Ngikhuluma nje, ngitsandza kusho kutsi: Ndvunankhulu, lalela bantfu bakho.
