Ligia Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ushaya emabili emaGiants ngesikhatsi abhekene neDundee
I-Dundee Stars yavala ngaLesihlanu e-Elite League ngesikhatsi ibhekene ne-Belfast Giants ngekuncoba umdlalo wasekhaya nga-5-3 ngaMgcibelo.
EmaGiant atfola umchele wemagoli lamabili ngemuva kwekushaywa ngu-Patrick Dwyer na-Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan naJordan Cownie baletsa likhaya labalinganako ngaphambi kwekutsi Dwyer abuyisele buholi kumaGiants.
Francois Bouchard wahlanganisa simo se Dundee ngaphambi kwekutsi imigoco lemibili ya Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ivikele kuncoba kwabo.
Loku bekukwehluleka kwe-Elite League kwesitsatfu kulomnyaka lokwatfolwa ngulabo labadlala ku-Adam Keefe, labaphindze bacedza futsi bagcina sebaphumelele ekuhambiseni Dundee 2-1 eBelfast ngeLesihlanu ebusuku.
