Nancy Pelosi usola Brett Kavanaugh ngekutsi "uyindvodza lenemacebo," utsi akakulungele kuba seNkantolo lePhakeme.
Umholi welicembu lelicondzile le-Opposition Nancy Pelosi usola umengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme Brett Kavanaugh ngekutsi "uyindvodza lenemacebo" futsi utsi akasiyo intfo lenhle kutsi angahlala enkantolo.
Pelosi wenta lamavi enkhulumeni yakhe ngeMgcibelo eMkhosini weTexas Tribune e-Austin, eTexas.
"Angikwati kukubalekela kucabanga kutsi nangabe umfati enta ngalendlela, batawutsi uyahlanya", kusho Pelosi mayelana nekuphendvula kwakhe ngekubika kwaKavanaugh phambi kweKhomishini yeTemtsetfo ngeLesine.
Kavanaugh waphika ngekucindzeteleka kutsi abekadze ahlukunyetwa ngekwelicansi nguDkt Christine Blasey Ford ngesikhatsi basengemajaha.
Etincomeni takhe tekucala, Kavanaugh bekatfukutsela kakhulu, tikhatsi letinyenti bekacishe amemete futsi bekatfola kumatima kukhuluma ngesikhatsi akhuluma ngemndeni wakhe kanye neminyaka yakhe yasekolishi.
Waphindze walahla ngekucagela emaDemocrat kulelikomidi, watsi lamacala labekwe wona "kubulala bantfu ngendlela lengenangcondvo futsi lecondzene" lokwahlelwa ngema liberal labekhatsateke ngekutsi Hillary Clinton ulahlekelwe ngumengameli nga-2016.
Pelosi watsi ukholelwa kutsi bufakazi baKavanaugh bufakazela kutsi angeke akhone kusebenta eNkantolo lePhakeme ngobe unenkhani ngebaDemocrats.
"Ngicabanga kutsi utilahla yena ngekwenta leto tintfo kanye nangesimo sakhe sengcondvo ngaClinton kanye nemaDemocrats", kusho yena.
Pelosi waveta kutsi uyaphikisana nekutsi utawetama kumangalela uma avunywa, futsi uma emaDemocrats atfola emavoti lamanyenti eSigungu.
"Ngitawusho loku - uma angasho liciniso eNkantolo nobe e-FBI, angeke akhone kuba seNkantolo lePhakeme kuphela, kepha utawuba seNkantolo lapho akhona khona", kusho Pelosi.
Kavanaugh nyalo usengumajaji weNkantolo lePhakeme yase-D.C.
Pelosi wachubeka watsi njengemdemocratic bekakhatsateke ngesincumo saKavanaugh mayelana neMtsetfo weTemphilo nobe Roe v. Wade, ngobe bekabukwa njengalofuna bulungiswa lobunemtsetfo.
Ngesikhatsi sekubekwa kwakhe, Kavanaugh wagwema umbuto wekutsi utawugucula yini tincumo letitsite teNkantolo lePhakeme.
"Lesi akusiso sikhatsi sekutsi umuntfu lonelulaka futsi lonelubandlululo aye enkantolo futsi alindzele kutsi sitsi, 'Akukuhle yini loko,'" kusho Pelosi.
Futsi bafati kufanele bakwati kulawula loko.
Bekulihlazo lelisuka enhlitiyweni, intfukutselo leyayitsatsa tinyanga letinyenti neminyaka, futsi abengeke akhone kuyiveta ngaphandle kwekukhala.
"Sikhalela lusizi, " kusho Mnumzane Steinem kimi ngemuva kweminyaka lengu-45.
"Angikuboni loko kungakalungi, wena ucabanga kutsi kunjani?"
Wachubeka watsi: "Ngasitwa kakhulu ngulomunye wesifazane lobekahola likhaya, lowatsi naye uyakhala nakatfukutsele, kodvwa watfutfukisa indlela yekutsi nakatfukutsele acale kukhala, bese utsi kulona lokhuluma naye, 'Ungatsi ngiva buhlungu ngobe ngiyakhala.'
Bengitfukutsele kakhulu".
Ngemuva kwaloko wachubeka.
Ngicabanga kutsi loko kuhle kakhulu.
Tinyembeti takhe tikhombisa kutsi utfukutsele ngobe abengacondzisiswa kahle.
Lokunye lengikukhumbulako kakhulu emsebentini wami wekucala, ehhovisi lelibuswa ngemadvodza, ngesikhatsi ngikhala ngelulaka lolukhulu, bekukutsi intfombi lendzala - umphatsi lobekatfukutsele kakhulu futsi bengihlale ngikwesaba - ingibambe intamo ingihudvulele esitezi.
"Ungalokotsi ubonise kutsi uyakhala", washo njalo kimi.
"Abati kutsi utfukutsele.
Bacabanga kutsi uyahlupheka futsi utawujabula ngobe bacabanga kutsi baphumelele".
