Indlela Umncintiswano Wetekuhweba we-US-China longaba muhle ngayo eBeijing
Umdlalo wekucala wekuncintisana ngekuhwebelana emkhatsini weMelika neChina uyadzabukisa, futsi njengobe kulwa kusengakapheli, kungevani emkhatsini wemave lamabili kungahle kube lusito eBeijing esikhatsini lesidze, ngekusho kwetati.
Donald Trump, Mengameli waseMelika, wakhipha secwayiso sakhe sekucala ekucaleni kwalomnyaka ngekubeka umtselo etikwetintfo letibalulekile tase China letitsengiswa ngaphandle kufaka ekhatsi emapaneli elanga, insimbi ne aluminium.
Kukhuphuka lokukhulu kwacala kuleliviki ngenhlawulo lensha letsintsana netintfo letingu-$200 billion (£150 billion), ngalokusebenta kubeka umtselo kuhafu wato tonkhe tintfo letingeniswa eMelika nge China.
I-Beijing iphendvule ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi, muva nje iletse intsela lengaba ngu-5 kuya ku-10% etintfweni taseMelika letibita tigidzigidzi letinge-$60.
I-China seyicele kufana ne-USA, futsi umnotfo wesibili lomkhulu emhlabeni angeke ushintshe masinyane.
Kutjela iWashington kutsi iyekele kusho kutsi kufanele ilandzele intsandvo yayo, kodvwa kunikela ebaleni eMelika kutawuba lihlazo lelikhulu kuXi Jinping, umengameli waseChina.
Nanobe kunjalo, tati titsi uma iBeijing ingadlala kahle emakhadi ayo, kucindzeteleka kwekuncintisana kwe-US kungasekela iChina ngalokuhle esikhatsini lesidze ngekunciphisa kuncika kwemnotfo.
"Lokubuhlungu kutsi tincumo tepolitiki letisheshako te-Washington nobe i-Beijing tingenta simo lesenta kube netinkinga temnotfo emaveni lamabili sibe yingoti kakhulu kunaloko lababukeli labebakwati", kusho Abigail Grace, longumcwaningi lochumana nge-Asia lohlala e-Center for New American Security, lesinye sikhungo lesatiwako.
I-Syria 'ikulungele' kubuyela kwebabaleki, kusho iNdvuna yeTasekhaya
I-Syria itsi ikulungele kuvumela kutsi bakhoseli babuye ngekutitsandzela futsi iniketa lusito lwekwakha kabusha live lelibhujiswe timphi letineminyaka lengetulu kwayisikhombisa.
Akhuluma eMhlanganweni Wetive Letihlangene, iNdvuna Yetangaphandle Walid al-Moualem watsi timo eveni lakhe tiyachubeka nekutfutfuka.
"Lamuhla simo semhlaba sesisimeme futsi siphephile ngenca yetintfo letentekile ekulweni nebuphekula", kusho yena.
Hulumende uchubeka nekulungisa tindzawo letibhujiswe ngemasotja kute tibe nguloko lebetikuko ekucaleni.
Tonkhe letintfo setentekile ngenca yekubuyela kwalabo lababalekile emaveni abo ngekutitsandzela, lapho baphocelelwa khona kutsi bahambe ngenca yebuphekula kanye netincumo temnotfo letenta kuphila kwabo kwemalanga onkhe netindlela tabo tekuphila tibe ngumgomo.
