IYurophu icinisekisa kuncoba kwayo eRyder Cup eParis
Licembu lase Europe litfole iRyder Cup ngekuncoba licembu lase USA ngemaphuzu ekugcina langu 16.5 na 10.5 eLe Golf National ngaphandle kwe Paris, eFrance.
I-USA ilahlekelwe tikhatsi letisitfupha letilandzelanako emhlabatsini wase Europe futsi ayikaze iwine i-Ryder Cup eYurophu kusukela nga-1993.
I-Europe yatfola umklomelo wayo ngesikhatsi inhloko yelicembu laseDenmark Thomas Bjorn itfola emaphuzu langu-14.5 ladzingeka kuncoba i-United States.
Inkhanyeti yaseMelika Phil Mickelson, lebeyicitsa sikhatsi lesidze kulomdlalo, washaya inkatho yakhe yemanti emgodzini we par-3 wemgodzi we-16, wavuma kuncotjwa nguFrancesco Molinari.
Molinari wase-Italy wagcwala umfutfo, waba ngumunye webadlali labane labake baba ngu-5-0-0 kusukela kwacala lomdlalo nga-1979.
Umsubathi waseMelika Jordan Spieth wehlulwa 5&4 ngumdlali lophansi kakhulu ecenjini laseYurophu, Thorbjorn Olesen waseDenmark.
Umdlali lohamba embili emhlabeni Dustin Johnson ulahlekelwe ngu-2 kuya ku-1 ku-Ian Poulter waseNgilandi lobekangase adlale emdlalweni wakhe wekugcina we-Ryder Cup.
Umuntfu lowatiwako we Ryder Cup wesiphohlongo, Sergio Garcia wase Spain waba ngumuntfu wase Europe lowancoba ngalokuphelele ngemaphuzu emsebenti langu 25.5 kulomdlalo.
"Angivami kukhala kodvwa angikakhoni kumelana naloku lamuhla.
Bekungumnyaka lobumatima.
Ngibonga kakhulu Thomas ngekungikhetsa nekungetsemba.
Ngijabula kakhulu, ngijabula kakhulu kutsi lomntfwana wami sewuphindze waba khona.
"Kungumsebenti welithimba, futsi ngiyajabula kutsi ngingakhona kusita", kusho Garcia ngemuva kwekuncoba kweYurophu.
Waniketa lomsebenti wakhe kumlingani wakhe John Ram lowancoba tigolifu letatiwa kakhulu taseMelika Tiger Woods 2&1 emdlalweni munye ngeLisontfo.
"Kungijabulisa kakhulu kuncoba Tiger Woods, ngakhula ngimubuka", kusho Rahm loneminyaka lengu-23.
Woods ulahlekelwe yimidlalo yakhe lemine eFrance futsi nyalo unemlandvo we 13-21-3 wekubhala umlandvo wemsebenti we Ryder Cup.
Linani lelikhulu lemdlali lomkhulu lowake wancoba emacembu lamane layinhloko ngaphansi kwaJack Nicklaus.
Licembu laseMelika belisolo lifuna kufinyelela ebaleni lemidlalo yonkhe leliviki ngaphandle kwaPatrick Reed, Justin Thomas naTony Finau, labadlala igalofu lenkhulu kulo lonkhe lomdlalo.
Kwatsi ngemuva kwekudvumateka kwelicembu lakhe, umphatsi welicembu laseMelika Jim Furyk watsi: "Ngiyajabula ngalabantfu, balwa kamatima.
Kukhona sikhatsi lamuhla ekuseni lapho sihlupha khona iYurophu.
Sahlukana.
Hlonipha Thomas.
Bekangukaputeni lomuhle.
Bonkhe labadlali labangu-12 badlala kahle kakhulu.
Sitawutihlanganisa kabusha, ngisebente ne-PGA yaseMelika kanye neKomidi yetfu ye-Ryder Cup futsi sitawuchubeka.
Ngiyabatsandza labantfu labangu-12 futsi ngiyajabula kuba likaputeni.
Kufanele umhloniphe.
Besiphumelela".
Tindzawo letiphansi tekugcwala e Pinellas, Manatee nase Sarasota
Umbiko lomusha we Florida Fish and Wildlife Commission ukhombisa kwehla lokukhulu ekuhlanganeni kwe Red Tide etindzaweni tase Tampa Bay.
Ngekusho kwe-FWC, simo sekukhula lokungalingani sabikwa kusuka etindzaweni tase Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte nase Collier - lokukhombisa kwehla kwekugcwala.
Lendzawo ye Red Tide ihlanganisa emabanga langemakhilomitha lalikhulu nemashumi lamatsatfu elugwini lolusuka enyakatfo ye Pinellas kuya eningizimu ye Lee County.
Letigodzi titfolwa cishe emamayeleni langu-10 eningizimu yelwandle endzaweni yaseHillsborough, kepha kuletinye tindzawo tihlobene naleti letenteka evikini leliphelile.
Emagagasi labovu aphindze abonwa endzaweni yase Pasco.
Kugcwala lokukhulu noma lokuphasi kwelwandle endzaweni yase Pinellas kubikwe kuleliviki leliphelile, kugcwala lokuncane kuya kuphakeme endzaweni yase Hillsborough, kugcwala lokuphasi kuya kuphakeme endzaweni yase Manatee, kugcwala lokuphasi kuya kuphakeme endzaweni yase Sarasota, kugcwala lokuphasi kuya kulesisemkhatsini endzaweni yase Charlotte, kugcwala lokuphasi kuya kulesisemkhatsini endzaweni yase Lee, kanye nekugcwala lokuphasi endzaweni yase Collier.
Kucindzeteleka kwekuphefumula kuyachubeka kubikwa ePinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee nase Collier.
Kute umbiko wekucedzeka kwekuphefumula eNyakatfo Nshonalanga yeFlorida kuleliviki leliphelile.
